471086,108,2838,2,4,1,27,2,15 . Piyadassībuddhavaṃsavaṇṇanā 
471087,108,2839,2,19,1,142,13,"Sujātassa pana aparabhāge ito aṭṭhakappasatādhikasahassakappamatthake ekasmiṃ kappe piyadassī, atthadassī, {dhammadassī}ti tayo buddhā nibbattiṃsu. "
471088,108,2839,20,48,1,264,27,Tattha piyadassī nāma bhagavā pāramiyo pūretvā tusitapure nibbattitvā tato cavitvā sudhaññavatīnagare sudattassa nāma rañño aggamahesiyā candasadisavadanāya candādeviyā nāma kucchismiṃ paṭisandhiṃ gahetvā dasannaṃ māsānaṃ accayena varuṇuyyāne mātukucchito nikkhami. 
471089,108,2839,49,63,1,103,10,Tassa pana nāmaggahaṇadivase lokassa piyānaṃ pāṭihāriyavisesānaṃ dassitattā‘‘ piyadassī’’ tveva nāmamakaṃsu. 
471090,108,2839,64,68,1,38,4,So navavassasahassāni agāraṃ ajjhāvasi. 
471091,108,2839,69,75,1,60,6,Tassa kira sunimmalavimalagiribrahānāmakā tayo pāsādā ahesuṃ. 
471092,108,2839,76,81,1,71,5,Vimalāmahādevippamukhāni tettiṃsa itthisahassāni paccupaṭṭhitāni ahesuṃ. 
471093,108,2840,2,15,1,123,13,So cattāri nimittāni disvā vimalādeviyā kañcanaveḷe nāma putte uppanne ājaññarathena mahābhinikkhamanaṃ nikkhamitvā pabbaji. 
471094,108,2840,16,21,1,32,5,Ekā ca naṃ purisakoṭi anupabbaji. 
471095,108,2840,22,79,1,615,53,So tehi parivuto mahāpuriso cha māse padhānacariyaṃ caritvā visākhapuṇṇamāya varuṇabrāhmaṇagāme vasabhabrāhmaṇassa dhītāya dinnaṃ madhupāyāsaṃ paribhuñjitvā sālavane divāvihāraṃ vītināmetvā sujātājīvakena dinnā aṭṭha tiṇamuṭṭhiyo gahetvā kakudhabodhiṃ upasaṅkamitvā tepaññāsahatthavitthataṃ tiṇasantharaṃ santharitvā pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā sabbaññutaññāṇaṃ paṭivijjhitvā‘‘ anekajātisaṃsāran’’ ti udānaṃ udānetvā tattheva sattasattāhaṃ vītināmetvā attanā saha pabbajitānaṃ ariyadhammapaṭivedhasamatthataṃ ñatvā ākāsena tattha gantvā usabhavatīnagarasamīpe usabhavatuyyāne otaritvā bhikkhukoṭiparivuto dhammacakkaṃ pavattesi. 
