471800,108,3284,2,22,1,178,18,Phussassa buddhassa aparabhāge sāntarakappe tasmiñca kappe vītivatte ito ekanavutikappe vijitasabbakappo parahitaniratasaṅkappo sabbattha vipassī vipassī nāma satthā loke udapādi. 
471801,108,3284,23,41,1,211,18,So pāramiyo pūretvā anekaratanamaṇivisarasamujjotitabhavane tusitabhavane nibbattitvā tato cavitvā bandhumatīnagare anekabandhumato bandhumato rañño bandhumatiyā nāma aggamahesiyā kucchismiṃ paṭisandhiṃ aggahesi. 
471802,108,3284,42,53,1,97,11,So dasannaṃ māsānaṃ accayena kheme migadāye mātudarato asitanīradarājito puṇṇacando viya nikkhami. 
471803,108,3284,54,79,1,185,19,"Nāmaggahaṇadivase panassa lakkhaṇapāṭhakā ñātakā ca divā ca rattiñca antarantarā nimmisasañjanitandhakāravirahena visuddhaṃ passanti, vivaṭehi vā akkhīhi passatīti‘‘ vipassī’’ ti nāmamakaṃsu."
