473712,109,77,49,56,1,32,5,"Sakkā pana, bhante, upamaṃ kātunti?"
473713,109,77,57,65,1,30,5,"‘ Sakkā, bhikkhū’ ti bhagavā avoca. "
473714,109,77,66,77,1,86,9,"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhu, yojanaṃ āyāmena yojanaṃ vitthārena yojanaṃ ubbedhena mahāsāsaparāsi. "
473715,109,77,78,122,1,210,26,"Tato vassasatassa vassasahassassa accayena ekamekaṃ sāsapaṃ uddhareyya, khippataraṃ kho so, bhikkhu, mahāsāsaparāsi iminā upakkamena parikkhayaṃ pariyādānaṃ gaccheyya, na tveva kappo, evaṃ dīgho kho, bhikkhu, kappo’’ ti( saṃ. ni.2.128). "
473716,109,78,2,7,1,61,4,Svāyaṃ mahākappo saṃvaṭṭādivasena catuasaṅkhyeyyakappasaṅgaho. 
473717,109,78,8,10,1,14,2,Vuttampi cetaṃ–
473718,109,79,2,10,1,44,5,"‘ ‘ Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, kappassa asaṅkhyeyyāni. "
473719,109,79,11,13,1,16,2,Katamāni cattāri? 
473720,109,79,14,33,1,48,5,"Saṃvaṭṭo, saṃvaṭṭaṭṭhāyī, vivaṭṭo, vivaṭṭaṭṭhāyī’’ ti( a. ni.4.156). "
473721,109,80,2,11,1,60,6,"Tattha tayo saṃvaṭṭā– tejosaṃvaṭṭo, āposaṃvaṭṭo, vāyosaṃvaṭṭoti. "
473722,109,80,12,20,1,52,5,"Tisso saṃvaṭṭasīmā– ābhassarā, subhakiṇhā, vehapphalāti. "
473723,109,80,21,31,1,65,9,"Yadā hi kappo tejena saṃvaṭṭati, ābhassarato heṭṭhā agginā ḍayhati. "
473724,109,80,32,40,1,58,7,"Yadā āpena saṃvaṭṭati, subhakiṇhato heṭṭhā udakena vilīyati. "
