473726,109,80,50,60,1,87,8,"Vitthārato pana koṭisatasahassacakkavāḷaṃ vinassati, yaṃ buddhānaṃ āṇākkhettanti vuccati. "
473727,109,80,61,80,1,142,18,Tesu tīsu saṃvaṭṭesu yathākkamaṃ kappavināsakamahāmeghato yāva jālāya vā udakassa vā vātassa vā upacchedo idaṃ ekaṃ asaṅkhyeyyaṃ saṃvaṭṭo nāma. 
473728,109,80,81,92,1,143,10,"Kappavināsakajālādipacchedato yāva koṭisatasahassacakkavāḷaparipūrako sampattimahāmegho uṭṭhahati, idaṃ dutiyaṃ asaṅkhyeyyaṃ saṃvaṭṭaṭṭhāyī nāma. "
473729,109,81,2,11,1,86,8,"Sampattimahāmeghato yāva candimasūriyapātubhāvo, idaṃ tatiyaṃ asaṅkhyeyyaṃ vivaṭṭo nāma. "
473730,109,81,12,22,1,104,9,"Candimasūriyapātubhāvato yāva puna kappavināsakamahāmegho, idaṃ catutthaṃ asaṅkhyeyyaṃ vivaṭṭaṭṭhāyī nāma. "
473731,109,81,23,26,1,49,3,Imesu catusaṭṭhiantarakappasaṅgahaṃ vivaṭṭaṭṭhāyī. 
