473740,109,82,29,41,1,105,12,Kassa pana asaṅkhiyeti aññassa avuttattā kappassa ca vuttattā pakaraṇato kappānanti ayamattho viññāyateva. 
473741,109,82,42,50,1,56,8,Na hi vuttaṃ vajjetvā avuttassa kassaci gahaṇaṃ yuttanti. 
