473743,109,82,64,75,1,74,9,"{Asaṅkhiye}ti ettha saṅkhātuṃ na sakkāti asaṅkhiyā, gaṇanaṃ atikkantāti attho."
473744,109,82,76,85,1,38,5,‘‘ Asaṅkhyeyyanti eko gaṇanaviseso’’ ti eke. 
473745,109,82,86,99,1,142,12,"Te hi ekato paṭṭhāya mahābalakkhapariyosānāni ekūnasaṭṭhiṭṭhānāni vajjetvā dasamahābalakkhāni asaṅkhyeyyaṃ nāma, saṭṭhimaṭṭhānantaranti vadanti. "
473746,109,82,100,115,1,129,12,"Taṃ na yujjati, saṅkhyāṭhānantaraṃ nāma gaṇanaviseso, tassa asaṅkhyeyyabhāvābhāvato ekaṃ ṭhānantaraṃ asaṅkhyeyyañcāti viruddhametaṃ. "
473747,109,82,116,124,1,75,8,Nanu ca asaṅkhyabhāvena asaṅkhyeyyattepi tassa catubbidhabhāvo na yujjatīti? 
