473751,109,83,2,16,1,120,13,Atīte kira ekasmiṃ kappe taṇhaṅkaro medhaṅkaro saraṇaṅkaro dīpaṅkaroti cattāro sammāsambuddhā anukkamena loke uppajjiṃsu. 
473752,109,83,17,25,1,61,8,Tesu dīpaṅkarassa bhagavato kāle amaravatī nāma nagaraṃ ahosi. 
473753,109,83,26,53,1,218,24,"Tattha sumedho nāma brāhmaṇo paṭivasati ubhato sujāto mātito ca pitito ca, saṃsuddhagahaṇiko yāva sattamā kulaparivaṭṭā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena, abhirūpo dassanīyo pāsādiko paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgato. "
473754,109,83,54,60,1,48,6,So aññaṃ kammaṃ akatvā brāhmaṇasippameva uggaṇhi. 
473755,109,83,61,65,1,43,4,Tassa daharakāleyeva mātāpitaro kālamakaṃsu. 
