475252,109,696,2,47,1,357,37,Mahāsatto ekapadikamaggaṃ disvā‘‘ pabbajitānaṃ vasanaṭṭhānaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti maddiñca putte ca tattheva ṭhapetvā assamapadaṃ pavisitvā akkharāni oloketvā‘‘ sakkena dinnosmī’’ ti paṇṇasāladvāraṃ vivaritvā paviṭṭho khaggañca dhanuñca apanetvā sāṭake omuñcitvā isivesaṃ gahetvā kattaradaṇḍaṃ ādāya nikkhamitvā paccekabuddhasadisena upasamena dārakānaṃ santikaṃ agamāsi. 
