475274,109,700,51,134,1,372,54,"Tena‘‘ kahaṃ, bho brāhmaṇa, gacchasī’’ ti puṭṭho‘‘ vessantaramahārājassa santikan’’ ti vutte‘‘ addhā ayaṃ brāhmaṇo tassa putte vā deviṃ vā yācituṃ gacchatī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ mā kho, tvaṃ brāhmaṇa, tattha gañchi, sace gacchasi, ettheva te sīsaṃ chinditvā mayhaṃ sunakhānaṃ ghāsaṃ karissāmī’’ ti tena santajjito maraṇabhayabhīto‘‘ ahamassa pitarā pesito dūto,‘ taṃ ānessāmī’ ti āgato’’ ti musāvādaṃ abhāsi. "
