475798,109,926,44,79,1,311,31,Tadā bodhisattassa bhavanato tassa paricārikā nāgamāṇavikā taṃ sabbakāmadadaṃ maṇiratanaṃ ādāya yamunātīre vālukārāsimatthake ṭhapetvā tassobhāsena rattiyaṃ kīḷitvā aruṇuggamane tassa brāhmaṇassa mantasaddaṃ sutvā‘‘ supaṇṇo’’ ti saññāya bhayatajjitā maṇiratanaṃ aggahetvā pathaviyaṃ nimujjitvā nāgabhavanaṃ agamaṃsu. 
