475800,109,927,8,42,1,253,29,Tasmiṃ khaṇe so nesādabrāhmaṇo puttena saddhiṃ migavadhāya araññaṃ gacchanto tassa hatthe taṃ maṇiratanaṃ disvā‘‘ idaṃ bhūridattassa sabbakāmadadaṃ maṇiratanan’’ ti sañjānitvā taṃ gaṇhitukāmo tena saddhiṃ allāpasallāpaṃ katvā mantavādibhāvaṃ jānitvā evamāha–
475801,109,927,43,68,1,147,19,"‘‘ sace me tvaṃ imaṃ maṇiratanaṃ dassasi, evāhaṃ te mahānubhāvaṃ nāgaṃ dassessāmi, yaṃ tvaṃ gahetvā gāmanigamarājadhāniyo caranto bahudhanaṃ lacchasī’’ ti."
