475816,109,929,65,69,1,33,4,Aṭṭhīni cuṇṇiyamānāni viya ahesuṃ. 
475817,109,930,2,9,1,51,7,Puna naṅguṭṭhe gahetvā dussaṃ pothento viya pothesi. 
475818,109,930,10,17,1,54,6,Mahāsatto evarūpaṃ dukkhaṃ anubhontopi neva kujjhittha. 
475819,109,930,18,22,1,35,4,Aññadatthu attano sīlameva āvajjesi. 
475820,109,930,23,34,1,82,11,Iti so mahāsattaṃ dubbalaṃ katvā vallīhi peḷaṃ sajjetvā mahāsattaṃ tattha pakkhipi. 
475821,109,930,35,41,1,43,6,Sarīraṃ panassa mahantaṃ tattha na pavisati. 
475822,109,930,42,64,1,137,18,Atha naṃ paṇhiyā koṭṭento pavesetvā peḷaṃ ādāya ekaṃ gāmaṃ gantvā gāmamajjhe otāretvā‘‘ nāgassa naccaṃ daṭṭhukāmā āgacchantū’’ ti saddamakāsi. 
475823,109,930,65,67,1,29,2,Sakalagāmavāsino sannipatiṃsu. 
475824,109,930,68,79,1,48,7,Tasmiṃ khaṇe alampāyano‘‘ nikkhama mahānāgā’’ ti āha. 
475825,109,930,80,82,1,17,2,Mahāsatto cintesi–
475826,109,930,83,112,1,148,22,"‘‘ ajja mayā parisaṃ tosentena kīḷituṃ vaṭṭati, evaṃ alampāyano bahudhanaṃ labhitvā tuṭṭho maṃ vissajjessati, yaṃ yaṃ esa maṃ kāreti, taṃ taṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
475827,109,931,2,19,1,62,12,"Atha naṃ so peḷato nikkhamantaṃ‘‘ mahā hohī’’ ti āha, so mahā ahosi."
475828,109,931,20,59,1,267,33,"‘‘ Khuddako vaṭṭo viphaṇo ekaphaṇo dviphaṇo yāva sahassaphaṇo ucco nīco dissamānakāyo adissamānakāyo dissamānaupaḍḍhakāyo nīlo pīto lohito odāto mañjiṭṭho hohi, dhūmaṃ vissajjehi, jālasikhaṃ udakañca vissajjehī’’ ti vutte tena vuttaṃ taṃ taṃ ākāraṃ nimminitvā naccaṃ dassesi. "
475829,109,931,60,67,1,86,7,Taṃ disvā manussā acchariyabbhutacittajātā bahuṃ hiraññasuvaṇṇavatthālaṅkārādiṃ adaṃsu. 
475830,109,931,68,73,1,39,5,Iti tasmiṃ gāme satasahassamattaṃ labhi. 
475831,109,931,74,88,1,73,10,So kiñcāpi mahāsattaṃ gaṇhanto‘‘ sahassaṃ labhitvā taṃ vissajjessāmī’’ ti āha. 
475832,109,931,89,112,1,125,18,"Taṃ pana dhanaṃ labhitvā‘‘ gāmakepi tāva mayā ettakaṃ dhanaṃ laddhaṃ, nagare kira bahudhanaṃ labhissāmī’’ ti dhanalobhena na muñci. "
475833,109,932,2,30,1,234,25,"So tasmiṃ gāme kuṭumbaṃ saṇṭhapetvā ratanamayaṃ peḷaṃ kāretvā tattha mahāsattaṃ pakkhipitvā sukhayānakaṃ āruyha mahantena parivārena gāmanigamarājadhānīsu taṃ kīḷāpetvā bārāṇasiṃ pāpuṇi, nāgarājassa madhulājaṃ deti, abaddhasattuñca deti. "
475834,109,932,31,36,1,38,5,So gocaraṃ na gaṇhi avissajjanabhayena. 
475835,109,932,37,49,1,92,12,Gocaraṃ agaṇhantampi ca naṃ cattāro nagaradvāre ādiṃ katvā tattha tattha māsamattaṃ kīḷāpesi. 
475836,109,932,50,59,1,37,5,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ saṃsito akataññunā’’ tiādi. 
475837,109,933,2,18,1,113,13,Tattha {saṃsito}ti eso nāgo amukassa nigrodharukkhassa samīpe vammikamatthake sayitoti evaṃ ṭhānaṃ dassetvā kathito. 
475838,109,933,19,28,1,88,8,{Akataññunā}ti attanā kataṃ upakāraṃ ajānantena mittadubbhinā nesādabrāhmaṇenāti adhippāyo. 
475839,109,933,29,41,1,90,7,{Alampāyano}ti alampāyanavijjāparijappanena‘‘ alampāyano’’ ti evaṃ laddhanāmo ahituṇḍikabrāhmaṇo. 
475840,109,933,42,46,1,24,3,{Mamaggahī}ti maṃ aggahesi. 
475841,109,933,47,59,1,93,12,Kīḷeti maṃ tahiṃ tahin ti tattha tattha gāmanigamarājadhānīsu attano jīvikatthaṃ maṃ kīḷāpeti. 
475842,109,934,2,17,1,105,11,17. Tiṇatopi lahuko {mamā}ti attano jīvitapariccāgo tiṇasalākapariccāgatopi lahuko hutvā mama upaṭṭhātīti attho. 
475843,109,934,18,34,1,175,15,Pathavīuppatanaṃ {viyā}ti sīlavītikkamo pana catunahutādhikadviyojanasatasahassabahalāya mahāpathaviyā parivattanaṃ viya tatopi taṃ bhāriyataraṃ hutvā mayhaṃ upaṭṭhātīti dasseti. 
475844,109,935,2,16,1,109,11,18. Nirantaraṃ jātisatan ti mama jātīnaṃ anekasatampi anekasatāsupi jātīsu nirantarameva sīlassa avītikkamanahetu. 
475845,109,935,17,22,1,37,5,Mama jīvitaṃ cajeyyaṃ cajituṃ sakkomi. 
475846,109,935,23,35,1,85,12,Neva sīlaṃ pabhindeyyan ti sīlaṃ pana samādinnaṃ ekampi neva bhindeyyaṃ na vināseyyaṃ. 
475847,109,935,36,42,1,59,5,Catuddīpāna {hetū}ti cakkavattirajjasiriyāpi kāraṇāti dasseti. 
475848,109,936,2,36,1,207,24,"19. Idāni yadatthaṃ attano jīvitampi pariccajitvā tadā sīlameva rakkhitaṃ, tāya ca sīlarakkhāya tathā anatthakārakesu nesādaalampāyanabrāhmaṇesu cittassa aññathattaṃ na kataṃ, taṃ dassetuṃ‘‘ api cā’’ ti osānagāthamāha. "
475849,109,936,37,40,1,24,3,Taṃ heṭṭhā vuttatthameva. 
475850,109,937,2,15,1,113,13,Evaṃ pana mahāsatte ahituṇḍikahatthagate tassa mātā dussupinaṃ disvā puttañca tattha apassantī sokābhibhūtā ahosi. 
475851,109,937,16,38,1,151,18,Athassā jeṭṭhaputto sudassano taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā subhogaṃ‘‘ himavantaṃ gantvā pañcasu mahānadīsu sattasu mahāsaresu bhūridattaṃ upadhāretvā ehī’’ ti pahiṇi. 
475852,109,937,39,59,1,109,15,"Kāṇāriṭṭhaṃ‘‘ devalokaṃ gantvā sace devatāhi dhammaṃ sotukāmāhi bhūridatto tattha nīto, tato naṃ ānehī’’ ti pahiṇi. "
475853,109,937,60,73,1,73,8,Sayaṃ pana‘‘ manussaloke gavesissāmī’’ ti tāpasavesena nāgabhavanato nikkhami. 
475854,109,937,74,82,1,75,8,Accimukhī nāmassa vemātikā bhaginī bodhisatte adhimattasinehā taṃ anubandhi. 
475855,109,937,83,99,1,158,16,Taṃ maṇḍūkacchāpiṃ katvā jaṭantare pakkhipitvā mahāsattassa uposathakaraṇaṭṭhānaṃ ādiṃ katvā sabbattha gavesanto anukkamena bārāṇasiṃ patvā rājadvāraṃ agamāsi. 
475856,109,937,100,119,1,123,15,Tadā alampāyano rājaṅgaṇe mahājanassa majjhe rañño bhūridattassa kīḷaṃ dassetuṃ peḷaṃ vivaritvā‘‘ ehi mahānāgā’’ ti saññamadāsi. 
475857,109,938,2,13,1,92,10,Mahāsatto sīsaṃ nīharitvā olokento jeṭṭhabhātikaṃ disvā peḷato nikkhamma tadabhimukho pāyāsi. 
475858,109,938,14,17,1,24,3,Mahājano bhīto paṭikkami. 
475859,109,938,18,25,1,52,7,So gantvā taṃ abhivādetvā nivattitvā peḷameva pāvisi. 
475860,109,938,26,48,1,71,13,"Alampāyano‘‘ iminā ayaṃ tāpaso daṭṭho’’ ti saññāya‘‘ mā bhāyi, mā bhāyī’’ ti āha. "
475861,109,938,49,90,1,236,31,"Sudassano‘‘ ayaṃ nāgo mayhaṃ kiṃ karissati, mayā sadiso ahituṇḍiko nāma natthī’’ ti tena vādappaṭivādaṃ samuṭṭhāpetvā‘‘ tvaṃ imaṃ nāgaṃ gahetvā gajjasi, ahaṃ taṃ imāya maṇḍūkacchāpiyā icchanto nāsayissāmī’’ ti bhaginiṃ pakkositvā hatthaṃ pasāresi. "
475862,109,938,91,113,1,190,22,Sā tassa saddaṃ sutvā jaṭantare nipannā tikkhattuṃ maṇḍūkavassitaṃ vassitvā nikkhamitvā aṃsakūṭe nisīditvā uppatitvā tassa hatthatale tīṇi visabindūni pātetvā puna tassa jaṭantarameva pāvisi. 
475863,109,939,2,16,1,107,11,"Sudassano visabinduṃ dassetvā‘‘ idaṃ binduṃ sace pathaviyaṃ pātessati, osadhitiṇavanappatayo sabbe nassissanti. "
475864,109,939,17,25,1,53,7,"Sace ākāse khipissati, sattavassāni devo na vassissati. "
475865,109,939,26,60,1,229,28,"Sace udake pātessati, yāvatā tattha udakajātā pāṇā sabbe mareyyun’’ ti vatvā rājānaṃ saddahāpetuṃ tayo āvāṭe khaṇāpetvā ekaṃ nānābhesajjānaṃ pūresi, dutiyaṃ gomayassa, tatiyaṃ dibbosadhānañceva pūretvā majjhe āvāṭe visabinduṃ pakkhipi. "
475866,109,939,61,65,1,37,4,Taṅkhaṇaññeva dhūmāyitvā jālā uṭṭhahi. 
475867,109,939,66,70,1,27,4,Sā gantvā gomayāvāṭaṃ gaṇhi. 
475868,109,939,71,79,1,74,8,Tatopi jālā uṭṭhāya dibbosadhapuṇṇaṃ gahetvā dibbosadhāni jhāpetvā nibbāyi. 
475869,109,939,80,90,1,86,10,Alampāyanaṃ tattha āvāṭassa avidūre ṭhitaṃ usumā pharitvā sarīracchaviṃ uppāṭetvā gatā. 
475870,109,939,91,93,1,16,2,Setakuṭṭhī ahosi. 
475871,109,939,94,106,1,69,8,So bhayatajjito‘‘ nāgarājānaṃ vissajjemī’’ ti tikkhattuṃ vācaṃ nicchāresi. 
475872,109,939,107,118,1,106,10,Taṃ sutvā bodhisatto ratanapeḷāya nikkhamitvā sabbālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍitaṃ attabhāvaṃ māpetvā devalīḷāya ṭhito. 
475873,109,939,119,125,1,42,6,Sudassano ca accimukhī ca tatheva aṭṭhaṃsu. 
475874,109,940,2,8,1,52,6,Tato sudassano attano bhāgineyyabhāvaṃ rañño ārocesi. 
475875,109,940,9,39,1,192,25,"Taṃ sutvā rājā te āliṅgitvā sīse cumbitvā antepuraṃ netvā mahantaṃ sakkārasammānaṃ katvā bhūridattena saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ karonto‘‘ tāta, evaṃ mahānubhāvaṃ taṃ alampāyano kathaṃ gaṇhī’’ ti pucchi. "
475876,109,940,40,61,1,115,16,"So sabbaṃ vitthārena kathetvā‘‘ mahārāja, raññā nāma iminā niyāmena rajjaṃ kāretuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti mātulassa dhammaṃ desesi. "
475877,109,940,62,89,1,171,21,"Atha sudassano‘‘ mātula, mama mātā bhūridattaṃ apassantī kilamati, na sakkā amhehi idha papañcaṃ kātun’’ ti mātulaṃ āpucchitvā bhūridattaaccimukhīhi saddhiṃ nāgabhavanameva gato. "
475878,109,941,2,40,1,329,36,Atha tattha mahāpuriso gilānaseyyāya nipanno gilānapucchanatthaṃ āgatāya mahatiyā nāgaparisāya vede ca yaññe ca brāhmaṇe ca sambhāvetvā kāṇāriṭṭhe kathente taṃ vādaṃ bhinditvā nānānayehi dhammaṃ desetvā sīlasampadāya diṭṭhisampadāya ca patiṭṭhāpetvā yāvajīvaṃ sīlāni rakkhitvā uposathakammaṃ katvā āyupariyosāne saggapuraṃ pūresi. 
475879,109,942,2,6,1,37,4,Tadā mātāpitaro mahārājakulāni ahesuṃ. 
475880,109,942,7,27,1,150,14,"Nesādabrāhmaṇo devadatto, somadatto ānando, accimukhī uppalavaṇṇā, sudassano sāriputto, subhogo mahāmoggallāno, kāṇāriṭṭho sunakkhatto, bhūridatto lokanātho. "
475881,109,943,2,8,1,60,6,Tassa idhāpi sesapāramiyo heṭṭhā vuttanayeneva niddhāretabbā. 
475882,109,943,9,121,1,1257,103,"Idhāpi yojanasatike attano nāgabhavanaṭṭhāne soḷasahi nāgakaññāsahassehi cittarūpaṃ viya paricāriyamāno devalokasampattisadise nāgalokissariye ṭhitopi issariyamadaṃ akatvā anvaddhamāsaṃ mātāpituupaṭṭhānaṃ, kule jeṭṭhāpacāyanaṃ, sakalāya nāgaparisāya cātumahārājikaparisāya tāvatiṃsaparisāya ca samuṭṭhitapañhānaṃ taṃtaṃparisamajjhe kumudanālakalāpaṃ viya sunisitasatthena attano paññāsatthena tāvadeva pacchinditvā tesaṃ cittānukūladhammadesanā, vuttappakāraṃ bhogasampattiṃ pahāya attano sarīrajīvitanirapekkhaṃ caturaṅgasamannāgataṃ uposathādhiṭṭhānaṃ, tattha ca paṭiññāya visaṃvādanabhayena ahituṇḍikahatthagamanaṃ, tasmiñca mukhe visamissakheḷapātanaṃ naṅguṭṭhe gahetvā āviñchanaṃ kaḍḍhanaṃ bhūmiyaṃ ghaṃsanaṃ maddanaṃ pothananti evamādiṃ nānappakāravippakāraṃ karontepi evarūpaṃ mahādukkhaṃ anubhavatopi kujjhitvā olokanamattena taṃ chārikaṃ kātuṃ samatthassāpi sīlapāramiṃ āvajjitvā sīlakhaṇḍanabhayena īsakampi cittassa vikārābhāvo, dhanaṃ labhāpemīti vā tassa cittānuvattanaṃ, subhogena punānītassa akataññuno mittadubbhissa nesādabrāhmaṇassa sīlaṃ anadhiṭṭhahitvāpi akujjhanaṃ, kāṇāriṭṭhena kathitaṃ micchāvādaṃ bhinditvā anekapariyāyena dhammaṃ bhāsitvā nāgaparisāya sīlesu sammādiṭṭhiyañca patiṭṭhāpananti evamādayo bodhisattassa guṇānubhāvā vibhāvetabbā. "
475883,109,943,122,125,1,15,2,Tenetaṃ vuccati–
475884,109,943,126,139,1,47,7,‘‘ evaṃ acchariyā hete… pe… dhammassa anudhammato’’ ti. 
475885,109,944,2,4,1,32,2,Bhūridattacariyāvaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.
475886,109,945,2,4,1,25,2,3 . Campeyyanāgacariyāvaṇṇanā 
475887,109,946,2,26,1,150,17,"20. Tatiye {campeyyako}ti aṅgamagadharaṭṭhānaṃ antare campā nāma nadī, tassā heṭṭhā nāgabhavanampi avidūrabhavattā campā nāma, tattha jāto nāgarājā campeyyako. "
475888,109,946,27,36,1,76,9,Tadāpi dhammiko āsin ti tasmiṃ campeyyanāgarājakālepi ahaṃ dhammacārī ahosiṃ. 
475889,109,947,2,14,1,99,11,"Bodhisatto hi tadā campānāgabhavane nibbattitvā campeyyo nāma nāgarājā ahosi, mahiddhiko mahānubhāvo. "
475890,109,947,15,46,1,267,26,"So tattha nāgarajjaṃ kārento devarājabhogasampattisadisaissariyasampattiṃ anubhavanto pāramipūraṇassa anokāsabhāvato‘‘ kiṃ me imāya tiracchānayoniyā, uposathavāsaṃ vasitvā ito muccitvā sammadeva pāramiyo pūressāmī’’ ti tato paṭṭhāya attano pāsādeyeva uposathakammaṃ karoti. "
475891,109,947,47,51,1,46,4,Alaṅkatanāgamāṇavikā tassa santikaṃ āgacchanti. 
475892,109,947,52,67,1,78,11,So‘‘ idha me sīlassa antarāyo bhavissatī’’ ti pāsādato nikkhamitvā uyyāne nisīdati. 
475893,109,947,68,71,1,21,3,Tatrāpi tā āgacchanti. 
475894,109,947,72,74,1,10,2,So cintesi–
475895,109,947,75,94,1,113,13,"‘‘ idha me sīlassa saṃkileso bhavissati, ito nāgabhavanato nikkhamitvā manussalokaṃ gantvā uposathavāsaṃ vasissāmī’’ ti. "
475896,109,947,95,137,1,337,35,"So tato paṭṭhāya uposathadivasesu nāgabhavanā nikkhamitvā ekassa paccantagāmassa avidūre maggasamīpe vammikamatthake‘‘ mama cammādīhi atthikā cammādīni gaṇhantu, kīḷāsappaṃ vā kātukāmā kīḷāsappaṃ karontū’’ ti sarīraṃ dānamukhe vissajjetvā bhoge ābhujitvā nipanno uposathavāsaṃ vasati cātuddasiyaṃ pañcadasiyañca, pāṭipade nāgabhavanaṃ gacchati. "
475897,109,947,138,144,1,51,6,Tassevaṃ uposathaṃ karontassa dīgho addhā vītivatto. 
475898,109,948,2,44,1,252,31,"Atha bodhisatto sumanāya nāma attano aggamahesiyā‘‘ deva, tvaṃ manussalokaṃ gantvā uposathaṃ upavasasi, so ca sāsaṅko sappaṭibhayo’’ ti vutto maṅgalapokkharaṇitīre ṭhatvā‘‘ sace maṃ, bhadde, koci paharitvā kilamessati, imissā pokkharaṇiyā udakaṃ āvilaṃ bhavissati. "
475899,109,948,45,51,1,44,5,"Sace supaṇṇo gaṇhissati, udakaṃ pakkuthissati. "
475900,109,948,52,77,1,219,22,"Sace ahituṇḍiko gaṇhissati, udakaṃ lohitavaṇṇaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti tīṇi nimittāni tassā ācikkhitvā cātuddasīuposathaṃ adhiṭṭhāya nāgabhavanā nikkhamitvā tattha gantvā vammikamatthake nipajji sarīrasobhāya vammikaṃ sobhayamāno. "
475901,109,948,78,116,1,172,15,"Sarīrañhissa rajatadāmaṃ viya setaṃ ahosi, matthako rattakambalageṇḍuko viya, sarīraṃ naṅgalasīsappamāṇaṃ bhūridattakāle( jā.2.22.784 ādayo) pana ūruppamāṇaṃ, saṅkhapālakāle( jā.2.17.143 ādayo) ekadoṇikanāvappamāṇaṃ. "
475902,109,949,2,44,1,318,36,"Tadā eko bārāṇasimāṇavo takkasilaṃ gantvā alampāyanamantaṃ uggaṇhitvā tena maggena attano gāmaṃ gacchanto mahāsattaṃ disvā‘‘ kiṃ me tucchahatthena gāmaṃ gantuṃ, imaṃ nāgaṃ gahetvā gāmanigamarājadhānīsu kīḷāpento dhanaṃ uppādetvāva gamissāmī’’ ti cintetvā dibbosadhāni gahetvā dibbamantaṃ parivattetvā tassa santikaṃ agamāsi. "
475903,109,949,45,58,1,128,12,"Dibbamantaṃ sutakālato paṭṭhāya mahāsattassa kaṇṇesu tattasalākāpavesanakālo viya ahosi, matthake sikharena abhimanthiyamāno viya. "
475904,109,949,59,76,1,84,13,So‘‘ ko nu kho eso’’ ti bhogantarato sīsaṃ ukkhipitvā olokento ahituṇḍikaṃ disvā cintesi–
475905,109,949,77,107,1,163,21,"‘‘ mama visaṃ uggatejaṃ, sacāhaṃ kujjhitvā nāsāvātaṃ vissajjessāmi, etassa sarīraṃ bhusamuṭṭhi viya vippakirissati, atha me sīlaṃ khaṇḍaṃ bhavissati, na naṃ olokessāmī’’ ti. "
475906,109,949,108,114,1,46,6,So akkhīni nimmīletvā sīsaṃ bhogantare ṭhapesi. 
475907,109,949,115,125,1,89,9,Ahituṇḍikabrāhmaṇo osadhaṃ khāditvā mantaṃ parivattetvā kheḷaṃ mahāsattassa sarīre osiñci. 
475908,109,949,126,136,1,95,10,Osadhānañca mantassa ca ānubhāvena kheḷena phuṭṭhaphuṭṭhaṭṭhāne phoṭānaṃ uṭṭhānakālo viya ahosi. 
475909,109,950,2,18,1,131,16,Atha so naṅguṭṭhe gahetvā ākaḍḍhitvā dīghaso nipajjāpetvā ajapadena daṇḍena uppīḷetvā dubbalaṃ katvā sīsaṃ daḷhaṃ gahetvā nippīḷesi. 
475910,109,950,19,22,1,23,3,Mahāsatto mukhaṃ vivari. 
