476359,109,1107,2,13,1,102,11,Tena vuttaṃ anācāraṃ asahamānā devatā tassa tesañca soḷasasahassānaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ mukhaṃ viparivattesuṃ. 
476360,109,1107,14,21,1,68,7,Taṃ disvā diṭṭhamaṅgalikā mahāsattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā tamatthaṃ ārocesi. 
476361,109,1107,22,49,1,157,22,"Bodhisatto‘‘ tassa anācāraṃ asahantehi yakkhehi so vippakāro kato, api ca kho pana imaṃ ucchiṭṭhapiṇḍakaṃ tesaṃ mukhe āsiñcitvā taṃ vippakāraṃ vūpasamehī’’ ti āha. "
