476364,109,1107,61,96,1,250,27,"‘‘ tāta, imasmiṃ loke dakkhiṇeyyā nāma mātaṅgapaṇḍitasadisā bhavanti, na ime brāhmaṇā viya jātimattena, mantasajjhāyanamattena vā mānatthaddhā’’ ti vatvā ye tadā sīlādiguṇavisesayuttā jhānasamāpattilābhino ceva paccekabuddhā ca, tatthevassa pasādaṃ uppādesīti. "
