476381,109,1116,2,15,1,124,12,Tattha vicaranto {anukūlamhī}ti ucchiṭṭhadantakaṭṭhe attano jaṭāsu lagge tassa āgamanagavesanavasena gaṅgāya tīre anuvicaranto. 
476382,109,1116,16,27,1,88,10,Uddhaṃ me {assamaddasā}ti attano vasanaṭṭhānato uparisote mama assamaṃ paṇṇasālaṃ addakkhi. 
476383,109,1116,28,58,1,177,23,"Tattha maṃ {paribhāsetvā}ti mama assamaṃ āgantvā jātiṃ sutvā tatova paṭikkamitvā savanūpacāre ṭhatvā‘‘ nassa, vasala caṇḍāla, kāḷakaṇṇi mā idha vasī’’ tiādīni vatvā bhayena santajjetvā. "
476384,109,1116,59,93,1,166,24,"Abhisapi muddhaphālanan ti‘‘ sace jīvitukāmosi, ettova sīghaṃ palāyassū’’ ti vatvā‘‘ sace na pakkamissati, ito te sattame divase sattadhā muddhā phalatū’’ ti me abhisapaṃ adāsi. "
476385,109,1117,2,8,1,42,6,Kiṃ pana tassa abhisapena muddhā phalatīti? 
