476670,109,1225,2,16,1,114,9,85. Dasame {saṅkhapālo}tiādīsu ayaṃ saṅkhepattho– devabhogasampattisadisāya mahatiyā nāgiddhiyā samannāgatattā mahiddhiko. 
476671,109,1225,17,27,1,63,9,"Heṭṭhā dve, upari dveti catasso dāṭhā āvudhā etassāti dāṭhāvudho. "
476672,109,1225,28,30,1,26,2,Uggatejavisatāya ghoraviso. 
476673,109,1225,31,36,1,53,5,Nāgayonisiddhāhi dvīhi jivhāhi samannāgatoti dvijivho. 
476674,109,1225,37,50,1,90,9,Mahānubhāvānampi urena gamanato‘‘ uragā’’ ti laddhanāmānaṃ nāgānaṃ adhipatibhāvato uragādhibhū. 
476675,109,1226,2,11,1,74,6,86. Dvinnaṃ maggānaṃ vinivijjhitvā sandhibhāvena gataṭṭhānasaṅkhāte catuppathe. 
476676,109,1226,12,15,1,49,3,Aparāparaṃ mahājanasañcaraṇaṭṭhānabhūte mahāmagge. 
476677,109,1226,16,20,1,50,4,Tato eva mahājanasamākiṇṇabhāvena nānājanasamākule. 
476678,109,1226,21,28,1,55,7,Idāni vakkhamānānaṃ catunnaṃ aṅgānaṃ vasena caturo aṅge. 
476679,109,1226,29,34,1,39,4,"Adhiṭṭhāya adhiṭṭhahitvā, citte ṭhapetvā. "
476680,109,1226,35,51,1,135,15,"Yadāhaṃ saṅkhapālo nāma yathāvuttarūpo nāgarājā homi, tadā heṭṭhā vuttappakāre ṭhāne vāsaṃ uposathavāsavasena nivāsaṃ akappayiṃ kappesiṃ. "
476681,109,1227,2,20,1,213,18,Mahāsatto hi dānasīlādipuññapasuto hutvā bodhipariyesanavasena aparāparaṃ devamanussagatīsu saṃsaranto kadāci devabhogasadisasampattike nāgabhavane nibbattitvā saṅkhapālo nāma nāgarājā ahosi mahiddhiko mahānubhāvo. 
476682,109,1227,21,32,1,93,11,So gacchante kāle tāya sampattiyā vippaṭisārī hutvā manussayoniṃ patthento uposathavāsaṃ vasi. 
476683,109,1227,33,82,1,370,39,"Athassa nāgabhavane vasantassa uposathavāso na sampajjati, sīlaṃ saṃkilissati, tena so nāgabhavanā nikkhamitvā kaṇhavaṇṇāya nadiyā avidūre mahāmaggassa ca ekapadikamaggassa ca antare ekaṃ vammikaṃ parikkhipitvā uposathaṃ adhiṭṭhāya cātuddasapannarasesu samādinnasīlo‘‘ mama cammādīni atthikā gaṇhantū’’ ti attānaṃ dānamukhe vissajjetvā nipajjati, pāṭipade nāgabhavanaṃ gacchati. "
476684,109,1227,83,95,1,49,7,"Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ punāparaṃ yadā homi, saṅkhapālo’’ tiādi. "
476685,109,1227,96,99,1,19,3,Tassattho vutto eva. 
476686,109,1228,2,20,1,96,10,87. Yaṃ panettha chaviyā {cammenā}tiādikaṃ‘‘ caturo aṅge adhiṭṭhāyā’’ ti vuttaṃ caturaṅgādhiṭṭhānadassanaṃ. 
476687,109,1228,21,25,1,30,4,Chavicammāni hi idha ekamaṅgaṃ. 
476688,109,1228,26,33,1,64,7,Evaṃ uposathavāsaṃ vasantassa mahāsattassa dīgho addhā vītivatto. 
476689,109,1229,2,64,1,412,49,"Athekadivasaṃ tasmiṃ tathā sīlaṃ samādiyitvā nipanne soḷasa bhojaputtā‘‘ maṃsaṃ āharissāmā’’ ti āvudhahatthā araññe carantā kiñci alabhitvā nikkhamantā taṃ vammikamatthake nipannaṃ disvā‘‘ mayaṃ ajja godhāpotakampi na labhimhā, imaṃ nāgarājānaṃ vadhitvā khādissāmā’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ mahā kho panesa gayhamāno palāyeyyāti yathānipannakaṃyeva naṃ bhogesu sūlehi vijjhitvā dubbalaṃ katvā gaṇhissāmā’’ ti sūlāni ādāya upasaṅkamiṃsu. "
476690,109,1229,65,80,1,186,15,Bodhisattassāpi sarīraṃ mahantaṃ ekadoṇikanāvappamāṇaṃ vaṭṭetvā ṭhapitasumanapupphadāmaṃ viya jiñjukaphalasadisehi akkhīhi jayasumanapupphasadisena ca sīsena samannāgataṃ ativiya sobhati. 
476691,109,1229,81,133,1,369,43,So tesaṃ soḷasannaṃ janānaṃ padasaddena bhogantarato sīsaṃ nīharitvā rattakkhīni ummīletvā te sūlahatthe āgacchante disvā‘‘ ajja mayhaṃ manoratho matthakaṃ pāpuṇissatī’’ ti attānaṃ dānamukhe niyyātetvā‘‘ ime mama sarīraṃ sattīhi koṭṭetvā chiddāvachiddaṃ karonte na olokessāmī’’ ti attano sīlakhaṇḍabhayena daḷhaṃ adhiṭṭhānaṃ adhiṭṭhahitvā sīsaṃ bhogantare eva pavesetvā nipajji. 
476692,109,1230,2,25,1,212,23,Atha naṃ te upagantvā naṅguṭṭhe gahetvā ākaḍḍhantā bhūmiyaṃ pātetvā tikhiṇasūlehi aṭṭhasu ṭhānesu vijjhitvā sakaṇṭakā kāḷavettayaṭṭhiyo pahāramukhehi pavesetvā aṭṭhasu ṭhānesu kājehi ādāya mahāmaggaṃ paṭipajjiṃsu. 
476693,109,1230,26,36,1,80,10,Mahāsatto sūlehi vijjhanato paṭṭhāya ekaṭṭhānepi akkhīni ummīletvā te na olokesi. 
476694,109,1230,37,47,1,70,9,Tassa aṭṭhahi kājehi ādāya nīyamānassa sīsaṃ olambitvā bhūmiṃ paharati . 
