476875,109,1309,31,32,1,5,1,Kasmā? 
476876,109,1309,33,46,1,123,11,"Sāmaññā samaṇabhāvā sīlamattatopi apagato parihīno ayaṃ, tathā hi ayaṃ hirīsukkadhammajahito pajahitahirisaṅkhātasukkadhammo. "
