476878,109,1309,63,73,1,83,8,"{Parantihī}ti paranto paccanto nivāsabhūto etesaṃ atthīti parantino, sīmantarikavāsino. "
476879,109,1309,74,80,1,52,6,Tehi parantīhi aṭavikehi paccantadeso khobhito ahosi. 
476880,109,1309,81,102,1,166,18,"Taṃ paccantakopaṃ nisedhetuṃ vūpasametuṃ gacchanto mama pitā kururājā‘‘ tāta somanassakumāra, mayhaṃ sāmikaṃ uggatāpanaṃ ghoratapaṃ paramasantindriyaṃ jaṭilaṃ mā pamajji. "
476881,109,1309,103,122,1,128,16,"So hi amhākaṃ sabbakāmadado, tasmā yadicchakaṃ cittaruciyaṃ tassa cittānukūlaṃ pavattehi anuvattehī’’ ti tadā maṃ anusāsīti dasseti. "
476882,109,1310,2,51,1,275,36,"14. Tamahaṃ gantvānupaṭṭhānan ti pitu vacanaṃ anatikkanto taṃ kūṭatāpasaṃ upaṭṭhānatthaṃ gantvā taṃ sākavatthusmiṃ udakaṃ āsiñcantaṃ disvā‘‘ paṇṇiko ayan’’ ti ca ñatvā kacci te, gahapati, kusalan ti, gahapati, te sarīrassa kacci kusalaṃ kusalameva, tathā hi sākavatthusmiṃ udakaṃ āsiñcasi. "
476883,109,1310,52,68,1,103,15,"Kiṃ vā tava hiraññaṃ vā suvaṇṇaṃ vā āharīyatu, tathā hi paṇṇikavuttiṃ anutiṭṭhasīti idaṃ vacanaṃ abhāsiṃ. "
