477190,109,1440,99,109,1,70,9,Yaṃ brāhmaṇo paccupādī bhisāni yasmā tumhākaṃ ācariyo bhisāni alabhīti. 
477191,109,1440,110,116,1,38,5,Sakko isigaṇaṃ vanditvā devalokaṃ gato. 
477192,109,1440,117,122,1,56,5,Isigaṇopi jhānābhiññāyo nibbattetvā brahmalokūpago ahosi. 
477193,109,1441,2,32,1,252,22,"Tadā upakañcanādayo cha bhātaro sāriputtamoggallānamahākassapaanuruddhapuṇṇaānandattherā, bhaginī uppalavaṇṇā, dāsī khujjuttarā, dāso citto gahapati, rukkhadevatā sātāgiro, vāraṇo pālileyyanāgo, vānaro madhuvāsiṭṭho, sakko kāḷudāyī, mahākañcanatāpaso lokanātho. "
477194,109,1442,2,9,1,61,7,Tassa idhāpi heṭṭhā vuttanayeneva dasa pāramiyo niddhāretabbā. 
477195,109,1442,10,16,1,67,6,Tathā accantameva kāmesu anapekkhatādayo guṇānubhāvā vibhāvetabbāti. 
477196,109,1443,2,4,1,27,2,Bhisacariyāvaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.
477197,109,1444,2,4,1,24,2,5 . Soṇapaṇḍitacariyāvaṇṇanā 
477198,109,1445,2,11,1,59,5,42. Pañcame nagare {brahmavaḍḍhane}ti brahmavaḍḍhananāmake nagare. 
477199,109,1445,12,15,1,19,2,{Kulavare}ti aggakule. 
477200,109,1445,16,19,1,20,2,{Seṭṭhe}ti pāsaṃsatame. 
477201,109,1445,20,23,1,19,2,{Mahāsāle}ti mahāsāre. 
477202,109,1445,24,28,1,23,4,Ajāyahan ti ajāyiṃ ahaṃ. 
477203,109,1445,29,59,1,234,24,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– tasmiṃ kāle‘‘ brahmavaḍḍhanan’’ ti laddhanāme bārāṇasinagare yadā homi bhavāmi paṭivasāmi, tadā abhijātasampattiyā uditoditabhāvena agge vijjāvatasampattiyā seṭṭhe asītikoṭivibhavatāya mahāsāle brāhmaṇakule ahaṃ uppajjinti. "
477204,109,1446,2,15,1,132,12,Tadā hi mahāsatto brahmalokato cavitvā brahmavaḍḍhananagare asītikoṭivibhavassa aññatarassa brāhmaṇamahāsālassa putto hutvā nibbatti. 
477205,109,1446,16,26,1,51,6,Tassa nāmaggahaṇadivase‘‘ soṇakumāro’’ ti nāmaṃ kariṃsu. 
477206,109,1446,27,39,1,104,12,Tassa padasā gamanakāle aññopi satto brahmalokā cavitvā bodhisattassa mātuyā kucchimhi paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
477207,109,1446,40,50,1,42,6,Tassa jātassa‘‘ nandakumāro’’ ti nāmaṃ kariṃsu. 
477208,109,1446,51,69,1,166,14,Tesaṃ uggahitavedānaṃ sabbasippanipphattippattānaṃ vayappattānaṃ rūpasampadaṃ disvā tuṭṭhahaṭṭhā mātāpitaro‘‘ gharabandhanena bandhissāmā’’ ti paṭhamaṃ soṇakumāraṃ āhaṃsu–
477209,109,1446,70,86,1,68,9,"‘‘ tāta, te patirūpakulato dārikaṃ ānessāma, tvaṃ kuṭumbaṃ paṭipajjāhī’’ ti. "
477210,109,1447,2,21,1,105,13,"Mahāsatto ‘‘ alaṃ mayhaṃ gharāvāsena, ahaṃ yāvajīvaṃ tumhe paṭijaggitvā tumhākaṃ accayena pabbajissāmī’’ ti āha. "
477211,109,1447,22,34,1,85,12,Mahāsattassa hi tadā tayopi bhavā ādittaṃ agāraṃ viya aṅgārakāsu viya ca upaṭṭhahiṃsu. 
477212,109,1447,35,40,1,57,5,Visesato panesa nekkhammajjhāsayo nekkhammādhimutto ahosi. 
477213,109,1447,41,147,1,707,85,"Tassa adhippāyaṃ ajānantā te punappunaṃ kathentāpi tassa cittaṃ alabhitvā nandakumāraṃ āmantetvā‘‘ tāta, tena hi tvaṃ kuṭumbaṃ paṭipajjāhī’’ ti vatvā tenāpi‘‘ nāhaṃ mama bhātarā chaḍḍitakheḷaṃ sīsena ukkhipāmi, ahampi tumhākaṃ accayena bhātarā saddhiṃ pabbajissāmī’’ ti vutte‘‘ ime evaṃ taruṇā kāme jahanti, kimaṅgaṃ pana mayanti sabbeva pabbajissāmā’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ tāta, kiṃ vo amhākaṃ accayena pabbajjāya, sabbe saheva pabbajāmā’’ ti vatvā ñātīnaṃ dātabbayuttakaṃ datvā dāsajanaṃ bhujissaṃ katvā rañño ārocetvā sabbaṃ dhanaṃ vissajjetvā mahādānaṃ pavattetvā cattāropi janā brahmavaḍḍhananagarā nikkhamitvā himavantappadese padumapuṇḍarīkamaṇḍitaṃ mahāsaraṃ nissāya ramaṇīye vanasaṇḍe assamaṃ māpetvā pabbajitvā tattha vasiṃsu. "
477214,109,1447,148,150,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ– 
477215,109,1448,2,4,1,0,0,43.
477216,109,1449,2,10,1,44,6,"‘ ‘ Tadāpi lokaṃ disvāna, andhībhūtaṃ tamotthaṭaṃ; "
477217,109,1450,2,8,1,45,5,"Cittaṃ bhavato patikuṭati, tuttavegahataṃ viya. "
477218,109,1451,2,4,1,0,0,44.
477219,109,1452,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Disvāna vividhaṃ pāpaṃ, evaṃ cintesahaṃ tadā; "
477220,109,1453,2,8,1,42,5,"Kadāhaṃ gehā nikkhamma, pavisissāmi kānanaṃ. "
477221,109,1454,2,4,1,0,0,45.
477222,109,1455,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Tadāpi maṃ nimantiṃsu, kāmabhogehi ñātayo; "
477223,109,1456,2,9,1,46,6,"Tesampi chandamācikkhiṃ, mā nimantetha tehi maṃ. "
477224,109,1457,2,4,1,0,0,46.
477225,109,1458,2,13,1,43,8,"‘ ‘ Yo me kaniṭṭhako bhātā, nando nāmāsi paṇḍito; "
477226,109,1459,2,8,1,42,5,"Sopi maṃ anusikkhanto, pabbajjaṃ samarocayi. "
477227,109,1460,2,4,1,0,0,47.
477228,109,1461,2,14,1,40,9,"‘ ‘ Ahaṃ soṇo ca nando ca, ubho mātāpitā mama; "
477229,109,1462,2,11,1,45,6,"Tadāpi bhoge chaḍḍetvā, pāvisimhā mahāvanan’’ ti. "
477230,109,1463,2,14,1,85,10,"Tattha {tadāpī}ti yadā ahaṃ brahmavaḍḍhananagare soṇo nāma brāhmaṇakumāro ahosiṃ, tadāpi. "
477231,109,1463,15,22,1,59,6,Lokaṃ {disvānā}ti sakalampi sattalokaṃ paññācakkhunā passitvā. 
477232,109,1463,23,30,1,64,6,Andhībhūtan ti paññācakkhuvirahena andhajātaṃ andhabhāvaṃ pattaṃ. 
477233,109,1463,31,35,1,42,4,Tamotthaṭan ti avijjandhakārena abhibhūtaṃ. 
477234,109,1463,36,48,1,123,11,Cittaṃ bhavato {patikuṭatī}ti jātiādisaṃvegavatthupaccavekkhaṇena kāmādibhavato mama cittaṃ saṅkuṭati sannilīyati na visarati. 
477235,109,1463,49,60,1,82,9,"Tuttavegahataṃ {viyā}ti tuttaṃ vuccati ayokaṇṭakasīso dīghadaṇḍo, yo patodoti vuccati. "
477236,109,1463,61,76,1,131,14,"Tena vegasā abhihato yathā hatthājānīyo saṃvegappatto hoti, evaṃ mama cittaṃ tadā kāmādīnavapaccavekkhaṇena saṃvegappattanti dasseti. "
477237,109,1464,2,17,1,171,15,Disvāna vividhaṃ pāpan ti gehaṃ āvasantehi gharāvāsanimittaṃ chandadosādivasena karīyamānaṃ nānāvidhaṃ pāṇātipātādipāpakammañceva tannimittañca nesaṃ lāmakabhāvaṃ passitvā. 
477238,109,1464,18,45,1,177,22,Evaṃ cintesahaṃ {tadā}ti‘‘ kadā nu kho ahaṃ mahāhatthī viya ayabandhanaṃ gharabandhanaṃ chinditvā gehato nikkhamanavasena vanaṃ pavisissāmī’’ ti evaṃ tadā soṇakumārakāle cintesiṃ ahaṃ. 
477239,109,1464,46,83,1,255,28,"Tadāpi maṃ {nimantiṃsū}ti na kevalaṃ ayogharapaṇḍitādikāleyeva, atha kho tadāpi tasmiṃ soṇakumārakālepi maṃ mātāpituādayo ñātayo kāmabhogino kāmajjhāsayā‘‘ ehi, tāta, imaṃ asītikoṭidhanaṃ vibhavaṃ paṭipajja, kulavaṃsaṃ patiṭṭhāpehī’’ ti uḷārehi bhogehi nimantayiṃsu. "
477240,109,1464,84,106,1,190,20,"Tesampi chandamācikkhin ti tesampi mama ñātīnaṃ tehi kāmabhogehi mā maṃ nimantayitthāti attano chandampi ācikkhiṃ, pabbajjāya ninnajjhāsayampi kathesiṃ, yathājjhāsayaṃ paṭipajjathāti adhippāyo. "
477241,109,1465,2,45,1,176,21,Sopi maṃ anu {sikkhanto}ti‘‘ ime kāmā nāma appassādā bahudukkhā bahūpāyāsā’’ tiādinā( ma. ni.1.234;2.43-45; pāci.417) nayena nānappakāraṃ kāmesu ādīnavaṃ paccavekkhitvā yathāhaṃ sīlādīni sikkhanto pabbajjaṃ rocesiṃ. 
477242,109,1465,46,57,1,83,9,Sopi nandapaṇḍito tatheva tassa nekkhammena maṃ anusikkhanto pabbajjaṃ {samarocayī}ti. 
477243,109,1465,58,72,1,83,13,Ahaṃ soṇo ca nando {cā}ti tasmiṃ kāle soṇanāmako ahaṃ mayhaṃ kaniṭṭhabhātā nando cāti. 
477244,109,1465,73,97,1,120,17,"Ubho mātāpitā {mamā}ti‘‘ ime nāma puttakā evaṃ taruṇakālepi kāme jahanti, kimaṅgaṃ pana mayan’’ ti uppannasaṃvegā mātāpitaro ca. "
477245,109,1465,98,116,1,184,17,Bhoge {chaḍḍetvā}ti asītikoṭivibhavasamiddhe mahā bhoge anapekkhacittā kheḷapiṇḍaṃ viya pariccajitvā mayaṃ cattāropi janā himavantappadese mahāvanaṃ nekkhammajjhāsayena pavisimhāti attho. 
477246,109,1466,2,14,1,101,12,Pavisitvā ca te tattha ramaṇīye bhūmibhāge assamaṃ māpetvā tāpasapabbajjāya pabbajitvā tattha vasiṃsu. 
477247,109,1466,15,20,1,41,5,Te ubhopi bhātaro mātāpitaro paṭijaggiṃsu. 
477248,109,1466,21,45,1,177,19,Tesu nandapaṇḍito‘‘ mayā ābhataphalāphalāneva mātāpitaro khādāpessāmī’’ ti hiyyo ca purimagocaragahitaṭṭhānato ca yāni tāni avasesāni phalāphalāni pātova ānetvā mātāpitaro khādāpeti. 
477249,109,1466,46,53,1,52,7,Te tāni khāditvā mukhaṃ vikkhāletvā uposathikā honti. 
477250,109,1466,54,62,1,75,8,Soṇapaṇḍito pana dūraṃ gantvā madhuramadhurāni supakkāni āharitvā upanāmeti. 
477251,109,1466,63,85,1,100,16,"Atha naṃ te‘‘ tāta, kaniṭṭhena ābhatāni mayaṃ khāditvā uposathikā jātā, idāni no attho natthī’’ ti vadanti. "
477252,109,1466,86,108,1,150,19,"Iti tassa phalāphalāni paribhogaṃ na labhanti vinassanti, punadivasādīsupi tathevāti, evaṃ so pañcābhiññatāya dūrampi gantvā āharati, te pana na khādanti. "
477253,109,1467,2,5,1,22,3,Atha mahāsatto cintesi–
477254,109,1467,6,33,1,146,20,"‘‘ mātāpitaro sukhumālā, nando ca yāni tāni apakkāni duppakkāni phalāphalāni āharitvā khādāpeti, evaṃ sante ime na ciraṃ pavattissanti, vāressāmi nan’’ ti. "
477255,109,1467,34,55,1,114,15,"Atha naṃ āmantetvā‘‘ nanda, ito paṭṭhāya phalāphalaṃ āharitvā mamāgamanaṃ patimānehi, ubho ekatova khādāpessāmā’’ ti āha. "
477256,109,1467,56,64,1,61,8,Evaṃ vuttepi attano puññaṃ paccāsīsanto na tassa vacanamakāsi. 
477257,109,1467,65,100,1,178,26,"Mahāsatto taṃ upaṭṭhānaṃ āgataṃ‘‘ na tvaṃ paṇḍitānaṃ vacanaṃ karosi, ahaṃ jeṭṭho, mātāpitaro ca mameva bhāro, ahameva ne paṭijaggissāmi, tvaṃ ito aññattha yāhī’’ ti tassa accharaṃ pahari. "
477258,109,1468,2,28,1,203,25,So tena paṇāmito tattha ṭhātuṃ asakkonto taṃ vanditvā mātāpitūnaṃ tamatthaṃ ārocetvā attano paṇṇasālaṃ pavisitvā kasiṇaṃ oloketvā taṃdivasameva aṭṭha ca samāpattiyo pañca ca abhiññāyo nibbattetvā cintesi–
477259,109,1468,29,49,1,149,17,"‘‘ kiṃ nu kho ahaṃ sinerupādato ratanavālukaṃ āharitvā mama bhātu paṇṇasālāpariveṇaṃ ākiritvā khamāpessāmi, udāhu anotattato udakaṃ āharitvā khamāpessāmi? "
477260,109,1468,50,102,1,339,44,"Atha vā me bhātā devatāvasena khameyya, cattāro mahārājāno sakkañca devarājānaṃ ānetvā khamāpessāmi, evaṃ pana na sobhissati, ayaṃ kho manojo brahmavaḍḍhanarājā sakalajambudīpe aggarājā, taṃ ādiṃ katvā sabbe rājāno ānetvā khamāpessāmi, evaṃ sante mama bhātu guṇo sakalajambudīpaṃ avattharitvā gamissati, cando viya sūriyo viya ca paññāyissatī’’ ti. "
477261,109,1469,2,40,1,232,30,So tāvadeva iddhiyā gantvā brahmavaḍḍhananagare tassa rañño nivesanadvāre otaritvā‘‘ eko tāpaso tumhe daṭṭhukāmo’’ ti rañño ārocāpetvā tena katokāso tassa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ ahaṃ attano balena sakalajambudīpe rajjaṃ gahetvā tava dassāmī’’ ti.
477262,109,1469,41,56,1,67,9,"‘‘ Kathaṃ pana tumhe, bhante, sakalajambudīpe rajjaṃ gahetvā dassathā’’ ti?"
477263,109,1469,57,99,1,231,31,"‘‘ Mahārāja, kassaci vadhacchedaṃ akatvā attano iddhiyāva gahetvā dassāmī’’ ti mahatiyā senāya saddhiṃ taṃ ādāya kosalaraṭṭhaṃ gantvā nagarassa avidūre khandhāvāraṃ nivesetvā‘‘ yuddhaṃ vā no detu, vase vā vattatū’’ ti kosalarañño dūtaṃ pāhesi. "
477264,109,1469,100,129,1,219,27,"Tena kujjhitvā yuddhasajjena hutvā nikkhantena saddhiṃ yuddhe āraddhe attano iddhānubhāvena yathā dvinnaṃ senānaṃ pīḷanaṃ na hoti, evaṃ katvā yathā ca kosalarājā tassa vase vattati, evaṃ vacanapaṭivacanaharaṇehi saṃvidahi. "
477265,109,1469,130,136,1,55,6,Etenupāyena sakalajambudīpe rājāno tassa vase vattāpesi. 
477266,109,1470,2,7,1,36,5,So tena parituṭṭho nandapaṇḍitaṃ āha–
477267,109,1470,8,42,1,241,23,"‘‘ bhante, tumhehi yathā mayhaṃ paṭiññātaṃ, tathā kataṃ, bahūpakārā me tumhe, kimahaṃ tumhākaṃ karissāmi, ahañhi te sakalajambudīpe upaḍḍharajjampi dātuṃ icchāmi, kimaṅgaṃ pana hatthiassarathamaṇimuttāpavāḷarajatasuvaṇṇadāsidāsaparijanaparicchedan’’ ti? "
477268,109,1470,43,72,1,152,23,"Taṃ sutvā nandapaṇḍito‘‘ na me te, mahārāja, rajjena attho, nāpi hatthiyānādīhi, api ca kho te raṭṭhe asukasmiṃ nāma assame mama mātāpitaro pabbajitvā vasanti. "
477269,109,1470,73,102,1,185,24,"Tyāhaṃ upaṭṭhahanto ekasmiṃ aparādhe mama jeṭṭhabhātikena soṇapaṇḍitena nāma mahesinā paṇāmito, svāhaṃ taṃ ādāya tassa santikaṃ gantvā khamāpessāmi, tassa me tvaṃ khamāpane sahāyo hohī’’ ti. "
477270,109,1470,103,143,1,372,36,Rājā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā catuvīsatiakkhobhanī parimāṇāya senāya parivuto ekasatarājūhi saddhiṃ nandapaṇḍitaṃ purakkhatvā taṃ assamapadaṃ patvā caturaṅgulappadesaṃ muñcitvā ākāse ṭhitena kājena anotattato udakaṃ āharitvā pānīyaṃ paṭisāmetvā pariveṇaṃ sammajjitvā mātāpitūnaṃ āsannappadese nisinnaṃ jhānaratisamappitaṃ mahāsattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā nandapaṇḍito naṃ khamāpesi. 
477271,109,1470,144,152,1,80,8,Mahāsatto nandapaṇḍitaṃ mātaraṃ paṭicchāpetvā attanā yāvajīvaṃ pitaraṃ paṭijaggi. 
477272,109,1470,153,156,1,18,3,Tesaṃ pana rājūnaṃ–
477273,109,1471,2,11,1,38,7,"‘ ‘ Ānando ca pamodo ca, sadā hasitakīḷitaṃ; "
477274,109,1472,2,7,1,42,4,"Mātaraṃ paricaritvāna, labbhametaṃ vijānatā."
477275,109,1473,2,11,1,38,7,"‘ ‘ Ānando ca pamodo ca, sadā hasitakīḷitaṃ; "
477276,109,1474,2,7,1,42,4,"Pitaraṃ paricaritvāna, labbhametaṃ vijānato."
477277,109,1475,2,11,1,44,7,"‘ ‘ Dānañca peyyavajjañca, atthacariyā ca yā idha; "
477278,109,1476,2,9,1,48,6,"Samānattatā ca dhammesu, tattha tattha yathārahaṃ; "
477279,109,1477,2,9,1,40,6,"Ete kho saṅgahā loke, rathassāṇīva yāyato."
477280,109,1478,2,13,1,40,8,"‘ ‘ Ete ca saṅgahā nāssu, na mātā puttakāraṇā; "
477281,109,1479,2,10,1,43,7,"Labhetha mānaṃ pūjaṃ vā, pitā vā puttakāraṇā."
477282,109,1480,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Yasmā ca saṅgahā ete, sammapekkhanti paṇḍitā; "
477283,109,1481,2,10,1,46,7,"Tasmā mahattaṃ papponti, pāsaṃsā ca bhavanti te."
477284,109,1482,2,9,1,41,5,"‘ ‘ Brahmāti mātāpitaro, pubbācariyāti vuccare; "
477285,109,1483,2,8,1,38,5,"Āhuneyyā ca puttānaṃ, pajāya anukampakā."
477286,109,1484,2,12,1,44,8,"‘ ‘ Tasmā hi ne namasseyya, sakkareyya ca paṇḍito; "
477287,109,1485,2,10,1,39,6,"Annena atha pānena, vatthena sayanena ca; "
477288,109,1486,2,8,1,42,5,"Ucchādanena nhāpanena, pādānaṃ dhovanena ca."
477289,109,1487,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Tāya naṃ pāricariyāya, mātāpitūsu paṇḍitā; "
477290,109,1488,2,22,1,45,7,"Idheva naṃ pasaṃsanti, pecca sagge pamodatī’’ ti.( jā.2.20.176-183)– "
477291,109,1489,2,14,1,76,10,"Buddhalīḷāya dhammaṃ desesi, taṃ sutvā sabbepi te rājāno sabalakāyā pasīdiṃsu. "
477292,109,1489,15,30,1,84,11,Atha ne pañcasu sīlesu patiṭṭhāpetvā‘‘ dānādīsu appamattā hothā’’ ti ovaditvā vissajjesi. 
477293,109,1489,31,39,1,70,8,Te sabbepi dhammena rajjaṃ kāretvā āyupariyosāne devanagaraṃ pūrayiṃsu. 
477294,109,1489,40,57,1,117,13,Bodhisatto‘‘ ito paṭṭhāya mātaraṃ paṭijaggāhī’’ ti mātaraṃ nandapaṇḍitaṃ paṭicchāpetvā attanā yāvajīvaṃ pitaraṃ paṭijaggi. 
477295,109,1489,58,63,1,49,5,Te ubhopi āyupariyosāne brahmalokaparāyanā ahesuṃ. 
477296,109,1490,2,24,1,197,17,"Tadā mātāpitaro mahārājakulāni, nandapaṇḍito ānandatthero, manojo rājā sāriputtatthero, ekasatarājāno asītimahātherā ceva aññataratherā ca, catuvīsatiakkhobhanīparisā buddhaparisā, soṇapaṇḍito lokanātho. "
477297,109,1491,2,13,1,97,10,"Tassa kiñcāpi sātisayā nekkhammapāramī, tathāpi heṭṭhā vuttanayeneva sesapāramiyo ca niddhāretabbā. "
