477302,109,1495,2,39,1,220,27,"48. Chaṭṭhe kāsirājassa {atrajo}ti kāsirañño atrajo putto yadā homi, tadā mūgapakkhoti nāmena, temiyoti vadanti man ti temiyoti nāmena mūgapakkhavatādhiṭṭhānena‘‘ mūgapakkho’’ ti mātāpitaro ādiṃ katvā sabbeva maṃ vadantīti sambandho. "
477303,109,1495,40,69,1,173,22,"Mahāsattassa hi jātadivase sakalakāsiraṭṭhe devo vassi, yasmā ca so rañño ceva amaccādīnañca hadayaṃ uḷārena pītisinehena temayamāno uppanno, tasmā‘‘ temiyakumāro’’ ti nāmaṃ ahosi. "
477304,109,1496,2,11,1,64,5,49. Soḷasitthisahassānan ti soḷasannaṃ kāsirañño itthāgārasahassānaṃ. 
477305,109,1496,12,19,1,35,6,Na vijjati {pumo}ti putto na labbhati. 
477306,109,1496,20,28,1,44,7,"Na kevalañca putto eva, dhītāpissa natthi eva. "
477307,109,1496,29,56,1,230,24,"Ahorattānaṃ accayena, nibbatto {ahamekako}ti aputtakasseva tassa rañño bahūnaṃ saṃvaccharānaṃ atītattā anekesaṃ ahorattānaṃ apagamanena sakkadattiyo ahamekakova bodhipariyesanaṃ caramāno, tadā tassa putto hutvā uppannoti satthā vadati. "
477308,109,1497,2,10,1,63,7,Tatrāyaṃ anupubbikathā– atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ kāsirājā rajjaṃ kāresi. 
477309,109,1497,11,15,1,34,4,Tassa soḷasasahassā itthiyo ahesuṃ. 
477310,109,1497,16,24,1,43,8,Tāsu ekāpi puttaṃ vā dhītaraṃ vā na labhati. 
477311,109,1497,25,49,1,122,16,Nāgarā‘‘ amhākaṃ rañño vaṃsānurakkhako ekopi putto natthī’’ ti vippaṭisārī jātā sannipatitvā rājānaṃ‘‘ puttaṃ patthehī’’ ti āhaṃsu. 
477312,109,1497,50,61,1,54,7,Rājā soḷasasahassā itthiyo‘‘ puttaṃ patthethā’’ ti āṇāpesi. 
477313,109,1497,62,69,1,59,7,Tā candādīnaṃ upaṭṭhānādīni katvā patthentiyopi na labhiṃsu. 
477314,109,1497,70,77,1,67,7,Aggamahesī panassa maddarājadhītā candādevī nāma sīlasampannā ahosi. 
477315,109,1497,78,88,1,34,6,Rājā‘‘ tvampi puttaṃ patthehī’’ ti āha. 
477316,109,1497,89,110,1,130,16,"Sā puṇṇamadivase uposathikā hutvā attano sīlaṃ āvajjetvā‘‘ sacāhaṃ akhaṇḍasīlā, iminā me saccena putto uppajjatū’’ ti saccakiriyamakāsi. "
477317,109,1497,111,118,1,50,6,Tassā sīlatejena sakkassa āsanaṃ uṇhākāraṃ dassesi. 
477318,109,1497,119,184,1,434,52,"Sakko āvajjento taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā‘‘ candādeviyā puttapaṭilābhassa upāyaṃ karissāmī’’ ti tassā anucchavikaṃ puttaṃ upadhārento bodhisattaṃ tāvatiṃsabhavane nibbattitvā tattha yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā tato cavitvā uparidevaloke uppajjitukāmaṃ disvā tassa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ samma, tayi manussaloke uppanne pāramiyo ca te pūressanti, mahājanassa ca vuḍḍhi bhavissati, ayaṃ kāsirañño candā nāma aggamahesī puttaṃ pattheti, tassā kucchiyaṃ uppajjāhī’’ ti āha. "
477319,109,1498,2,14,1,58,8,So ‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā tassā kucchiyaṃ paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
477320,109,1498,15,28,1,120,13,Tassa sahāyā pañcasatā devaputtā khīṇāyukā devalokā cavitvā tasseva rañño amaccabhariyānaṃ kucchīsu paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhiṃsu. 
