477331,109,1499,2,10,1,31,5,50. Tasmiṃ khaṇe cattāro corā ānītā. 
477332,109,1499,11,30,1,162,16,"Rājā tesu ekassa sakaṇṭakāhi kasāhi pahārasahassaṃ āṇāpesi, ekassa saṅkhalikāya bandhitvā bandhanāgārappavesanaṃ, ekassa sarīre sattippahāradānaṃ, ekassa sūlāropanaṃ. "
477333,109,1499,31,51,1,120,16,Mahāsatto pitu kathaṃ sutvā saṃvegappatto hutvā‘‘ aho mama pitā rajjaṃ nissāya bhāriyaṃ nirayagāmikammaṃ karotī’’ ti cintesi. 
