477587,109,1590,2,4,1,24,2,8 . Saccatāpasacariyāvaṇṇanā 
477588,109,1591,2,16,1,98,12,"Aṭṭhame tāpaso {saccasavhayo}ti saccasaddena avhātabbo saccanāmako tāpaso yadā yasmiṃ kāle homi, tadā. "
477589,109,1591,17,33,1,135,16,Saccena lokaṃ pālesin ti attano avisaṃvādibhāvena sattalokaṃ jambudīpe tattha tattha sattanikāyaṃ pāpato nānāvidhā anatthato ca rakkhiṃ. 
477590,109,1591,34,50,1,175,16,Samaggaṃ janamakāsahan ti tattha tattha kalahaviggahavivādāpannaṃ mahājanaṃ kalahe ādīnavaṃ dassetvā sāmaggiyaṃ ānisaṃsakathanena samaggaṃ avivadamānaṃ sammodamānaṃ ahamakāsiṃ. 
477591,109,1592,2,10,1,73,7,Tadā hi bodhisatto bārāṇasiyaṃ aññatarasmiṃ brāhmaṇamahāsālakule nibbatti. 
477592,109,1592,11,20,1,28,5,Tassa‘‘ sacco’’ ti nāmaṃ kariṃsu. 
477593,109,1592,21,34,1,127,13,So vayappatto takkasilaṃ gantvā disāpāmokkhassa ācariyassa santike sippaṃ uggaṇhitvā nacirasseva sabbasippānaṃ nipphattiṃ patto. 
477594,109,1592,35,50,1,137,14,Ācariyena anuññāto bārāṇasiṃ paccāgantvā mātāpitaro vanditvā tehi abhinandiyamāno tesaṃ cittānurakkhaṇatthaṃ katipāhaṃ tesaṃ santike vasi. 
477595,109,1592,51,62,1,105,11,Atha naṃ mātāpitaro patirūpena dārena saṃyojetukāmā sabbaṃ vibhavajātaṃ ācikkhitvā gharāvāsena nimantesuṃ. 
477596,109,1593,2,46,1,496,43,Mahāsatto nekkhammajjhāsayo attano nekkhammapāramiṃ paribrūhetukāmo gharāvāse ādīnavaṃ pabbajjāya ānisaṃsañca nānappakārato kathetvā mātāpitūnaṃ assumukhānaṃ rodamānānaṃ aparimāṇaṃ bhogakkhandhaṃ anantaṃ yasaṃ mahantañca ñātiparivaṭṭaṃ pahāya mahānāgova ayasaṅkhalikaṃ gharabandhanaṃ chindanto nikkhamitvā himavantappadesaṃ pavisitvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā vanamūlaphalāphalehi yāpento nacirasseva aṭṭha samāpattiyo pañca ca abhiññāyo nibbattetvā jhānakīḷaṃ kīḷayamāno samāpattivihārena viharati. 
477597,109,1594,2,16,1,174,14,So ekadivasaṃ dibbacakkhunā lokaṃ olokento addasa sakalajambudīpe manusse yebhuyyena pāṇātipātādidasaakusalakammapathapasute kāmanidānaṃ kāmādhikaraṇaṃ aññamaññaṃ vivādāpanne. 
477598,109,1594,17,20,1,18,3,Disvā evaṃ cintesi–
477599,109,1594,21,38,1,97,14,"‘‘ na kho pana metaṃ patirūpaṃ, yadidaṃ ime satte evaṃ pāpapasute vivādāpanne ca disvā ajjhupekkhaṇaṃ. "
477600,109,1594,39,70,1,226,25,"Ahañhi‘ satte saṃsārapaṅkato uddharitvā nibbānathale patiṭṭhapessāmī’ ti mahāsambodhiyānaṃ paṭipanno, tasmā taṃ paṭiññaṃ avisaṃvādento yaṃnūnāhaṃ manussapathaṃ gantvā te te satte pāpato oramāpeyyaṃ, vivādañca nesaṃ vūpasameyyan’’ ti. "
477601,109,1595,2,30,1,269,28,Evaṃ pana cintetvā mahāsatto mahākaruṇāya samussāhito santaṃ samāpattisukhaṃ pahāya iddhiyā tattha tattha gantvā tesaṃ cittānukūlaṃ dhammaṃ desento kalahaviggahavivādāpanne satte diṭṭhadhammikañca samparāyikañca virodhe ādīnavaṃ dassetvā aññamaññaṃ samagge sahite akāsi. 
477602,109,1595,31,42,1,116,11,Anekākāravokārañca pāpe ādīnavaṃ vibhāvento tato satte vivecetvā ekacce dasasu kusalakammapathadhammesu patiṭṭhāpesi. 
477603,109,1595,43,54,1,114,10,Ekacce pabbājetvā sīlasaṃvare indriyaguttiyaṃ satisampajaññe pavivekavāse jhānābhiññāsu ca yathārahaṃ patiṭṭhāpesi. 
