477611,109,1601,2,4,1,24,2,9 . Vaṭṭapotakacariyāvaṇṇanā 
477612,109,1602,2,33,1,246,24,"72. Navame magadhe {vaṭṭapotako}tiādīsu ayaṃ saṅkhepattho– magadharaṭṭhe aññatarasmiṃ araññappadese vaṭṭakayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā aṇḍakosaṃ padāletvā aciranikkhantatāya taruṇo maṃsapesibhūto, tato eva ajātapakkho vaṭṭakacchāpako yadā ahaṃ kulāvake yeva homi. "
477613,109,1603,2,17,1,98,11,73. {Mukhatuṇḍakenāharitvā}ti mayhaṃ mātā attano mukhatuṇḍakena kālena kālaṃ gocaraṃ āharitvā maṃ poseti. 
477614,109,1603,18,38,1,192,19,Tassā phassena {jīvāmī}ti parisedanatthañceva paribhāvanatthañca sammadeva kālena kālaṃ mamaṃ adhisayanavasena phusantiyā tassā mama mātuyā sarīrasamphassena jīvāmi viharāmi attabhāvaṃ pavattemi. 
477615,109,1603,39,50,1,81,11,Natthi me kāyikaṃ balan ti mayhaṃ pana atitaruṇatāya kāyasannissitaṃ balaṃ natthi. 
477616,109,1604,2,9,1,37,3,74. {Saṃvacchare}ti saṃvacchare saṃvacchare. 
477617,109,1604,10,13,1,23,2,{Gimhasamaye}ti gimhakāle. 
477618,109,1604,14,27,1,123,12,"Sukkharukkhasākhānaṃ aññamaññaṃ saṅghaṭṭanasamuppannena agginā tasmiṃ padese davaḍāho padippati pajjalati, so tathā padīpito. "
477619,109,1604,28,56,1,274,26,Upagacchati amhākan ti mayhaṃ mātāpitūnañcāti amhākaṃ vasanaṭṭhānappadesaṃ attano patiṭṭhānassa asuddhassāpi suddhabhāvakaraṇena pāvanato {pāvako}ti ca gatamagge indhanassa bhasmabhāvāvahanato {kaṇhavattanī}ti ca laddhanāmo aggi vanarukkhagacche dahanto kālena kālaṃ upagacchati. 
477620,109,1605,2,23,1,102,11,"75. Evaṃ upagamanato tadāpi {saddāyanto}ti‘‘ dhamadhama’’ iti evaṃ saddaṃ karonto, anuravadassanañhetaṃ dāvaggino. "
477621,109,1605,24,34,1,84,8,{Mahāsikhī}ti pabbatakūṭasadisānaṃ indhanānaṃ vasena mahatiyo sikhā etassāti mahāsikhī. 
477622,109,1605,35,45,1,89,10,Anupubbena anukkamena taṃ araññappadesaṃ jhāpento dahanto aggi mama samīpaṭṭhānaṃ upāgami. 
477623,109,1606,2,12,1,53,6,76. {Aggivegabhayā}ti vegena āgacchato aggino bhayena bhītā. 
477624,109,1606,13,20,1,64,6,{Tasitā}ti cittutrāsasamuṭṭhitena kāyassa chambhitattena ca utrāsā. 
477625,109,1606,21,24,1,21,2,{Mātāpitā}ti mātāpitaro. 
477626,109,1606,25,32,1,80,7,Attānaṃ parimocayun ti agginā anupaddutaṭṭhānagamanena attano sotthibhāvamakaṃsu. 
477627,109,1606,33,39,1,53,6,Mahāsatto hi tadā mahāgeṇḍukappamāṇo mahāsarīro ahosi. 
