477733,109,1652,2,13,1,47,5,92. Ekādasame kaṇhadīpāyano {isī}ti evaṃnāmako tāpaso. 
477734,109,1652,14,48,1,272,30,Bodhisatto hi tadā dīpāyano nāma attano sahāyaṃ maṇḍabyatāpasaṃ sūle uttāsitaṃ upasaṅkamitvā tassa sīlaguṇena taṃ avijahanto tiyāmarattiṃ sūlaṃ nissāya ṭhito tassa sarīrato paggharitvā patitapatitehi lohitabindūhi sukkhehi kāḷavaṇṇasarīratāya‘‘ kaṇhadīpāyano’’ ti pākaṭo ahosi. 
477735,109,1652,49,56,1,75,5,"{Paropaññāsavassānī}ti sādhikāni paññāsavassāni, accantasaṃyoge upayogavacanaṃ. "
