477743,109,1653,31,35,1,46,4,Athassa ayonisomanasikārena anabhirati uppajji. 
477744,109,1653,36,69,1,240,27,"So taṃ vinodetumasakkontopi kammañca phalañca saddahitvā tāva mahantaṃ vibhavaṃ pahāya agārasmā nikkhamanto yaṃ pajahi, puna tadatthameva nivatto,‘‘ eḷamūgo capalo vatāyaṃ kaṇhadīpāyano’’ ti imaṃ apavādaṃ jigucchanto attano hirottappabhedabhayena. "
