477886,109,1705,2,11,1,47,5,105. Dvādasame sutasomo {mahīpatī}ti evaṃnāmo khattiyo. 
477887,109,1705,12,22,1,94,10,Mahāsatto hi tadā kururaṭṭhe indapatthanagare korabyassa rañño aggamahesiyā kucchimhi nibbatti. 
