477948,109,1735,2,30,1,237,26,Cattāri sahassāni dāpetvā ekañca sukhayānakaṃ datvā mahatā sakkārasammāneneva taṃ uyyojetvā mātāpitaro vanditvā‘‘ ahaṃ brāhmaṇena ābhataṃ saddhammaratanaṃ pūjetvā tassa ca sakkārasammānaṃ katvā āgamissāmīti porisādassa paṭiññaṃ datvā āgato. 
477949,109,1735,31,73,1,222,30,"Tattha yaṃ brāhmaṇassa kattabbaṃ paṭipajjitabbaṃ taṃ kataṃ, idāni porisādassa santikaṃ gamissāmī’’ ti vutvā‘‘ tena hi, tāta sutasoma, kiṃ nāmetaṃ kathesi, caturaṅginiyā senāya coraṃ gaṇhissāma, mā gaccha corassa santikan’’ ti yāciṃsu. "
477950,109,1735,74,89,1,94,11,Soḷasasahassā nāṭakitthiyo sesaparijanāpi‘‘ amhe anāthe katvā kuhiṃ gacchasi devā’’ ti parideviṃsu.
477951,109,1735,90,103,1,65,9,‘‘ Punapi kira rājā corassa santikaṃ gamissatī’’ ti ekakolāhalaṃ ahosi. 
477952,109,1736,2,55,1,354,42,"Mahāsatto ‘‘ paṭiññāya saccāpanaṃ nāma sādhūnaṃ sappurisānaṃ āciṇṇaṃ, sopi mamaṃ saddahitvā vissajjesi, tasmā gamissāmiyevā’’ ti mātāpitaro vanditvā sesajanaṃ anusāsetvā assumukhena nānappakāraṃ paridevantena itthāgārādinā janena anugato nagarā nikkhamma taṃ janaṃ nivattetuṃ magge daṇḍakena tiriyaṃ lekhaṃ katvā‘‘ imaṃ mama lekhaṃ mā atikkamiṃsū’’ ti vatvā agamāsi. "
477953,109,1736,56,66,1,94,10,Mahājano tejavato mahāsattassa āṇaṃ atikkamituṃ asakkonto mahāsaddena kanditvā roditvā nivatti. 
477954,109,1736,67,72,1,48,5,Bodhisatto āgatamaggeneva tassa santikaṃ agamāsi. 
477955,109,1736,73,83,1,39,6,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ apucchi maṃ porisādo’’ tiādi. 
477956,109,1737,2,40,1,210,31,"Tattha kiṃ tvaṃ icchasi nisajjan ti tvaṃ attano nagaraṃ gantuṃ mama hatthato nissajjanaṃ kiṃ icchasi, tvaṃ‘‘ mayā takkasilādīsu ciraparicito saccavādī cā’’ ti vadasi, tasmā yathā mati te kāhāmi, yathāruci te karissāmi. "
477957,109,1737,41,53,1,74,11,Yadi me tvaṃ {punehisī}ti sace puna tvaṃ ekaṃseneva mama santikaṃ āgamissasi. 
477958,109,1738,2,20,1,110,13,108. Paṇhe āgamanaṃ {mamā}ti pageva mama āgamanaṃ tassa porisādassa paṭissuṇitvā pātova āgamissāmīti paṭissavaṃ katvā. 
477959,109,1738,21,42,1,137,16,Rajjaṃ niyyātayiṃ {tadā}ti tadā porisādassa santikaṃ gantukāmo‘‘ idaṃ vo rajjaṃ paṭipajjathā’’ ti mātāpitūnaṃ tiyojanasatikaṃ rajjaṃ niyyātesiṃ. 
477960,109,1739,2,9,1,30,4,109. Kasmā pana rajjaṃ niyyātayinti? 
477961,109,1739,10,45,1,299,34,"Anussaritvā sataṃ dhamman ti yasmā pana paṭiññāya saccāpanaṃ nāma sataṃ sādhūnaṃ mahābodhisattānaṃ paveṇī kulavaṃso, tasmā taṃ saccapāramitādhammaṃ pubbakaṃ porāṇaṃ jinehi buddhādīhi sevitaṃ anussaritvā saccaṃ anurakkhanto tassa brāhmaṇassa dhanaṃ datvā attano jīvitaṃ pariccajitvā porisādaṃ upāgamiṃ. "
477962,109,1740,2,32,1,126,20,"110. Natthi me saṃsayo {tatthā}ti tasmiṃ porisādassa santikaṃ gamane‘‘ ayaṃ maṃ kiṃ nu kho ghātessati, udāhu no’’ ti mayhaṃ saṃsayo natthi."
477963,109,1740,33,57,1,183,20,‘‘ Caṇḍo sāhasiko mayā saddhiṃ ekasatakhattiye devatāya balikammakaraṇasajjo ekanteneva ghātessatī’’ ti jānanto eva kevalaṃ saccavācaṃ anurakkhanto attano jīvitaṃ pariccajitvā taṃ upāgamiṃ. 
477964,109,1740,58,71,1,87,11,"Yasmā cetadevaṃ, tasmā saccena me samo natthi, esā me paramatthabhāvappattā saccapāramīti. "
477965,109,1741,2,53,1,303,40,"Upāgate pana mahāsatte vikasitapuṇḍarīkapadumasassirikamassa mukhaṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ vigatamaraṇabhayo hutvā āgato, kissa nu kho esa ānubhāvo’’ ti cintento‘‘ tassa maññe dhammassa sutattā ayaṃ evaṃ tejavā nibbhayo ca jāto, ahampi taṃ sutvā tejavā nibbhayo ca bhavissāmī’’ ti sanniṭṭhānaṃ katvā porisādo mahāsattaṃ āha–"
477966,109,1741,54,67,1,68,9,‘‘ suṇoma satārahagāthāyo yāsaṃ savanatthaṃ tvaṃ attano nagaraṃ gato’’ ti. 
477967,109,1742,2,19,1,93,12,"Taṃ sutvā bodhisatto‘‘ ayaṃ porisādo pāpadhammo, imaṃ thokaṃ niggahetvā lajjāpetvā kathessāmī’’ ti–"
477968,109,1743,2,9,1,41,5,"‘ ‘ Adhammikassa luddassa, niccaṃ lohitapāṇino; "
477969,109,1744,2,23,1,49,8,"Natthi saccaṃ kuto dhammo, kiṃ sutena karissasī’’ ti.( jā.2.21.427)– "
477970,109,1745,2,7,1,47,5,Vatvā puna tena suṭṭhutaraṃ sañjātasavanādarena–
477971,109,1746,2,10,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Sutvā dhammaṃ vijānanti, narā kalyāṇapāpakaṃ; "
477972,109,1747,2,23,1,44,8,"Api gāthā suṇitvāna, dhamme me ramate mano’’ ti.( jā.2.21.444)– "
477973,109,1748,2,44,1,283,31,"Vutte ‘‘ ayaṃ ativiya sañjātādaro sotukāmo, handassa kathessāmī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ tena hi samma, sādhukaṃ suṇohi manasikarohī’’ ti vatvā nandabrāhmaṇena kathitaniyāmeneva gāthānaṃ sakkaccaṃ thutiṃ katvā chakāmāvacaradevaloke ekakolāhalaṃ katvā devatāsu sādhukāraṃ dadamānāsu mahāsatto porisādassa–"
477974,109,1749,2,11,1,38,6,"‘ ‘ Sakideva mahārāja, sabbhi hoti samāgamo; "
477975,109,1750,2,9,1,42,6,"Sā naṃ saṅgati pāleti, nāsabbhi bahusaṅgamo."
477976,109,1751,2,10,1,46,6,"‘ ‘ Sabbhireva samāsetha, sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
477977,109,1752,2,9,1,43,6,"Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, seyyo hoti na pāpiyo."
477978,109,1753,2,13,1,56,9,"‘ ‘ Jīranti ve rājarathā sucittā, attho sarīrampi jaraṃ upeti; "
477979,109,1754,2,12,1,59,9,"Satañca dhammo na jaraṃ upeti, santo have sabbhi pavedayanti."
477980,109,1755,2,14,1,58,10,"‘ ‘ Nabhañca dūre pathavī ca dūre, pāraṃ samuddassa tadāhu dūre; "
477981,109,1756,2,24,1,59,9,"Tato have dūrataraṃ vadanti, satañca dhammo asatañca rājā’’ ti.( jā.2.21.411-414)– "
477982,109,1757,2,5,1,15,2,Dhammaṃ kathesi. 
477983,109,1757,6,19,1,115,13,Tassa tena sukathitattā ceva attano ca puññānubhāvena gāthā suṇantasseva sakalasarīraṃ pañcavaṇṇāya pītiyā paripūri. 
477984,109,1757,20,43,1,126,17,"So bodhisatte muducitto hutvā‘‘ samma sutasoma, dātabbayuttakaṃ hiraññādiṃ na passāmi, ekekāya gāthāya ekekaṃ varaṃ dassāmī’’ ti āha. "
477985,109,1757,44,85,1,192,29,Atha naṃ mahāsatto‘‘ tvaṃ attanopi hitāni ajānanto parassa kiṃ nāma varaṃ dassasī’’ ti apasādetvā puna tena‘‘ varaṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti yācito sabbapaṭhamaṃ‘‘ ahaṃ cirakālaṃ taṃ arogaṃ passeyyan’’ ti varaṃ yāci. 
477986,109,1757,86,107,1,151,17,So‘‘ ayaṃ idāni me vadhitvā maṃsaṃ khāditukāmassa mahānatthakarassa mayhameva jīvitamicchatī’’ ti tuṭṭhamānaso vañcetvā varassa gahitabhāvaṃ ajānanto adāsi. 
477987,109,1757,108,117,1,81,9,Mahāsatto hi upāyakusalatāya tassa ciraṃ jīvitukāmatāpadesena attano jīvitaṃ yāci. 
477988,109,1757,118,143,1,153,19,"Atha‘‘ parosataṃ khattiyānaṃ jīvitaṃ dehī’’ ti dutiyaṃ varaṃ, tesaṃ sake raṭṭhe paṭipādanaṃ tatiyaṃ varaṃ, manussamaṃsakhādanato viramaṇaṃ catutthaṃ varaṃ yāci. "
477989,109,1757,144,165,1,119,16,So tīṇi varāni datvā catutthaṃ varaṃ adātukāmo‘‘ aññaṃ varaṃ gaṇhāhī’’ ti vatvāpi mahāsattena nippīḷiyamāno tampi adāsiyeva. 
477990,109,1758,2,30,1,249,28,Atha bodhisatto porisādaṃ nibbisevanaṃ katvā teneva rājāno mocāpetvā bhūmiyaṃ nipajjāpetvā dārakānaṃ kaṇṇato suttavaṭṭi viya saṇikaṃ rajjuyo nīharitvā porisādena ekaṃ tacaṃ āharāpetvā pāsāṇena ghaṃsitvā saccakiriyaṃ katvā tesaṃ hatthatalāni makkhesi. 
477991,109,1758,31,35,1,28,4,Taṅkhaṇaṃ eva phāsukaṃ ahosi. 
477992,109,1758,36,86,1,403,45,Dvīhatīhaṃ tattheva vasitvā te aroge kāretvā tehi saddhiṃ abhijjanakasabhāvaṃ mittasanthavaṃ kāretvā tehi saddhiṃ taṃ bārāṇasiṃ netvā rajje patiṭṭhāpetvā‘‘ appamattā hothā’’ ti te rājāno attano attano nagaraṃ pesetvā indapatthanagarato āgatāya attano caturaṅginiyā senāya parivuto attano nagaraṃ gato tuṭṭhapamuditena nāgarajanena samparivāriyamāno antepuraṃ pavisitvā mātāpitaro vanditvā mahātalaṃ abhiruhi. 
477993,109,1759,2,16,1,129,14,Atha mahāsatto cha dānasālāyo kāretvā devasikaṃ mahādānāni pavattento sīlāni paripūrento uposathaṃ upavasanto pāramiyo anubrūhesi. 
477994,109,1759,17,28,1,95,11,Tepi rājāno mahāsattassa ovāde ṭhatvā dānādīni puññāni katvā āyupariyosāne saggapuraṃ pūrayiṃsu. 
477995,109,1760,2,25,1,200,16,"Tadā porisādo aṅgulimālatthero ahosi, kāḷahatthiamacco sāriputtatthero, nandabrāhmaṇo ānandatthero, rukkhadevatā mahākassapatthero, rājāno buddhaparisā, mātāpitaro mahārājakulāni, sutasomamahārājā lokanātho. "
477996,109,1761,2,7,1,55,5,Tassa heṭṭhā vuttanayeneva sesapāramiyopi niddhāretabbā. 
477997,109,1761,8,23,1,76,6,Tathā alīnasattucariyāvaṇṇanāya( cariyā aṭṭha.2.74 ādayo) viya mahāsattassa guṇānubhāvā vibhāvetabbāti. 
477998,109,1762,2,4,1,34,2,Mahāsutasomacariyāvaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā. 
477999,109,1763,2,4,1,20,2,Saccapāramī niṭṭhitā.
478000,109,1764,2,4,1,24,2,13 . Suvaṇṇasāmacariyāvaṇṇanā 
478001,109,1765,2,24,1,124,18,111. Terasame sāmo yadā vane āsin ti himavantasmiṃ migasammatāya nāma nadiyā tīre mahati araññe sāmo nāma tāpasakumāro yadā ahosi. 
478002,109,1765,25,35,1,97,9,Sakkena {abhinimmito}ti sakkassa devānamindassa upadesasampattiyā jātattā sakkena nibbattito janito. 
478003,109,1765,36,47,1,80,10,Tatrāyaṃ anupubbikathā– atīte bārāṇasito avidūre nadiyā tīre eko nesādagāmo ahosi. 
478004,109,1765,48,52,1,33,4,Tattha jeṭṭhanesādassa putto jāto. 
478005,109,1765,53,61,1,27,4,Tassa‘‘ dukūlo’’ ti nāmamakaṃsu. 
478006,109,1765,62,69,1,48,7,Tassā eva nadiyā paratīrepi eko nesādagāmo ahosi. 
478007,109,1765,70,74,1,33,4,Tattha jeṭṭhanesādassa dhītā jātā. 
478008,109,1765,75,83,1,27,4,Tassā‘‘ pārikā’’ ti nāmamakaṃsu. 
478009,109,1765,84,89,1,40,5,Te ubhopi brahmalokato āgatā suddhasattā. 
478010,109,1765,90,96,1,59,5,Tesaṃ vayappattānaṃ anicchamānānaṃyeva āvāhavivāhaṃ kariṃsu. 
478011,109,1765,97,105,1,63,8,Te ubhopi kilesasamuddaṃ anotaritvā brahmāno viya ekato vasiṃsu. 
478012,109,1765,106,111,1,32,5,Na ca kiñci nesādakammaṃ karonti. 
478013,109,1766,2,25,1,109,16,"Atha dukūlaṃ mātāpitaro‘‘ tāta, tvaṃ nesādakammaṃ na karosi, neva gharāvāsaṃ icchasi, kiṃ nāma karissasī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
478014,109,1766,26,36,1,43,6,So‘‘ tumhesu anujānantesu pabbajissāmī’’ ti āha.
478015,109,1766,37,45,1,20,4,‘‘ Tena hi pabbajāhī’’ ti. 
478016,109,1766,46,67,1,164,20,"Dvepi janā himavantaṃ pavisitvā yasmiṃ ṭhāne migasammatā nāma nadī himavantato otaritvā gaṅgaṃ pattā, taṃ ṭhānaṃ gantvā gaṅgaṃ pahāya migasammatābhimukhā abhiruhiṃsu. "
478017,109,1766,68,74,1,40,5,Tadā sakkassa bhavanaṃ uṇhākāraṃ dassesi. 
478018,109,1766,75,84,1,64,9,Sakko taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā vissakammunā tasmiṃ ṭhāne assamaṃ māpesi. 
478019,109,1766,85,94,1,85,9,Te tattha gantvā pabbajitvā sakkadattiye assame kāmāvacaramettaṃ bhāvetvā paṭivasiṃsu. 
478020,109,1766,95,99,1,34,4,Sakkopi tesaṃ upaṭṭhānaṃ āgacchati. 
478021,109,1767,2,53,1,290,36,"So ekadivasaṃ‘‘ tesaṃ cakkhū parihāyissantī’’ ti ñatvā upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ bhante, vo cakkhūnaṃ antarāyo paññāyati, paṭijagganakaṃ puttaṃ laddhuṃ vaṭṭati, jānāmi tumhākaṃ suddhacittataṃ, tasmā pārikāya utunikāle nābhiṃ hatthena parāmaseyyātha , evaṃ vo putto jāyissati, so vo upaṭṭhahissatī’’ ti vatvā pakkāmi. "
478022,109,1767,54,63,1,77,9,Dukūlapaṇḍito taṃ kāraṇaṃ pārikāya ācikkhitvā tassā utunikāle nābhiṃ parāmasi. 
478023,109,1767,64,78,1,113,13,"Tadā bodhisatto devalokā cavitvā tassā kucchimhi paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi, sā dasamāsaccayena suvaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ puttaṃ vijāyi. "
478024,109,1767,79,88,1,38,5,Tenevassa‘‘ suvaṇṇasāmo’’ ti nāmaṃ kariṃsu. 
478025,109,1767,89,100,1,130,11,Taṃ aparabhāge vaḍḍhitvā soḷasavassuddesikampi mātāpitaro rakkhantā assame nisīdāpetvā sayameva vanamūlaphalāphalatthāya gacchanti. 
478026,109,1768,2,28,1,256,26,Athekadivasaṃ vane phalāphalaṃ ādāya nivattitvā assamapadato avidūre meghe uṭṭhite rukkhamūlaṃ pavisitvā vammikamatthake ṭhitānaṃ sarīrato sedagandhamissake udake tasmiṃ vammikabile ṭhitassa āsivisassa nāsāpuṭaṃ paviṭṭhe āsiviso kujjhitvā nāsāvātena pahari. 
478027,109,1768,29,34,1,38,5,Dve andhā hutvā paridevamānā viraviṃsu. 
478028,109,1768,35,54,1,100,14,"Atha mahāsatto‘‘ mama mātāpitaro aticirāyanti, kā nu kho tesaṃ pavattī’’ ti paṭimaggaṃ gantvā saddamakāsi. "
478029,109,1768,55,80,1,142,19,"Te tassa saddaṃ sañjānitvā paṭisaddaṃ katvā puttasinehena‘‘ tāta sāma, idha paripantho atthi, mā āgamī’’ ti vatvā saddānusārena sayameva samāgamiṃsu. "
478030,109,1768,81,130,1,237,33,"So‘‘ kena vo kāraṇena cakkhūni vinaṭṭhānī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ tāta, mayaṃ na jānāma, deve vassante rukkhamūle vammikamatthake ṭhitā, atha na passāmā’’ ti vuttamatte eva aññāsi‘‘ tattha āsivisena bhavitabbaṃ, tena kuddhena nāsāvāto vissaṭṭho bhavissatī’’ ti. "
478031,109,1769,2,22,1,130,14,"Atha ‘‘ mā cintayittha, ahaṃ vo paṭijaggissāmī’’ ti mātāpitaro assamaṃ netvā tesaṃ rattiṭṭhānadivāṭṭhānādisañcaraṇaṭṭhāne rajjuke bandhi. "
478032,109,1769,23,46,1,189,18,"Tato paṭṭhāya te assame ṭhapetvā vanamūlaphalāphalāni āharati, pātova vasanaṭṭhānaṃ sammajjati, pānīyaṃ āharati, paribhojanīyaṃ upaṭṭhāpeti, dantakaṭṭhamukhodakāni datvā madhuraphalāphalaṃ deti. "
478033,109,1769,47,57,1,87,10,Tehi mukhe vikkhālite sayaṃ paribhuñjitvā mātāpitaro vanditvā tesaṃ avidūreyeva acchati–
478034,109,1769,58,68,1,26,6,‘‘ kiṃ nu kho ime āṇāpentī’’ ti. 
478035,109,1769,69,79,1,64,8,"Visesena ca mettaṃ bahulamakāsi, tenassa sattā appaṭikkūlā ahesuṃ . "
478036,109,1769,80,89,1,57,8,"Yathā cassa sattā, evaṃ sattānaṃ so bodhisatto appaṭikkūlo. "
478037,109,1769,90,101,1,98,11,Evaṃ so divase divase phalāphalatthāya araññaṃ gacchantopi āgacchantopi migagaṇaparivuto eva ahosi. 
478038,109,1769,102,115,1,147,12,"Sīhabyagghādivipakkhasattāpi tena saddhiṃ ativiya vissatthā, mettānubhāvena panassa vasanaṭṭhāne aññamaññaṃ tiracchānagatā muducittataṃ paṭilabhiṃsu. "
478039,109,1769,116,126,1,72,10,Iti so sabbattha mettānubhāvena abhīrū anutrāsī brahmā viya avero vihāsi. 
478040,109,1769,127,139,1,59,7,"Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ pavane sīhabyagghe ca, mettāyamupanāmayin’’ tiādi. "
478041,109,1770,2,17,1,130,13,"Tattha mettāyamupanāmayin ti ma -kāro padasandhikaro, mettābhāvanāya kurūrakammante sīhabyagghepi phari, pageva sesasatteti adhippāyo. "
478042,109,1770,18,27,1,58,8,"Atha vā mettā ayati pavattati etenāti mettāyo, mettābhāvanā. "
478043,109,1770,28,34,1,49,6,Taṃ mettāyaṃ upanāmayiṃ sattesu anodhiso upanesiṃ.
478044,109,1770,35,42,1,24,3,‘‘ Sīhabyagghehī’’ tipi pāṭho. 
478045,109,1770,43,66,1,152,19,"Tassattho– na kevalamahameva, atha kho pavane sīhabyagghehi, yasmiṃ mahāvane tadā ahaṃ viharāmi, tattha sīhabyagghehi saddhiṃ ahaṃ sattesu mettaṃ upanāmesiṃ. "
478046,109,1770,67,79,1,99,11,"Sīhabyagghāpi hi tadā mamānubhāvena sattesu mettacittataṃ paṭilabhiṃsu, pageva itare sattāti dasseti. "
