478090,109,1793,2,4,1,20,2,14 . Ekarājacariyāvaṇṇanā 
478091,109,1794,2,14,1,81,8,114. Cuddasame ekarājāti {vissuto}ti ekarājāti iminā anvatthanāmena jambudīpatale pākaṭo. 
478092,109,1795,2,9,1,52,7,Mahāsatto hi tadā bārāṇasirañño putto hutvā nibbatti. 
478093,109,1795,10,34,1,224,19,Vayappatto sabbasippanipphattiṃ patto hutvā pitu accayena rajjaṃ kārento kusalasīlācārasaddhāsutādianaññasādhāraṇaguṇavisesayogena pāramiparibhāvanena ca jambudīpatale adutiyattā padhānabhāvena ca‘‘ ekarājā’’ ti pakāsanāmo ahosi. 
478094,109,1795,35,51,1,218,14,Paramaṃ sīlaṃ {adhiṭṭhāyā}ti suparisuddhakāyikavācasikasaṃvarasaṅkhātañceva suparisuddhamanosamācārasaṅkhātañca paramaṃ uttamaṃ dasakusalakammapathasīlaṃ samādānavasena ca avītikkamanavasena ca adhiṭṭhahitvā anuṭṭhahitvā. 
478095,109,1795,52,62,1,85,10,Pasāsāmi mahāmahin ti tiyojanasatike kāsiraṭṭhe mahatiṃ mahiṃ anusāsāmi rajjaṃ kāremi. 
478096,109,1796,2,20,1,131,12,"115. {Dasakusalakammapathe}ti pāṇātipātāveramaṇi yāva sammādiṭṭhīti etasmiṃ dasavidhe kusalakammapathe, ete vā anavasesato samādāya vattāmi. "
478097,109,1796,21,43,1,193,19,"Catūhi {saṅgahavatthūhī}ti dānaṃ piyavacanaṃ atthacariyā samānattatāti imehi catūhi saṅgahavatthūhi saṅgaṇhanakāraṇehi yadā ekarājāti vissuto homi, tadā yathārahaṃ mahājanaṃ {saṅgaṇhāmī}ti sambandho. "
478098,109,1797,2,15,1,128,10,116. Evan ti dasakusalakammapathasīlaparipūraṇaṃ catūhi saṅgahavatthūhi mahājanasaṅgaṇhananti yathāvuttena iminā ākārena appamattassa. 
478099,109,1797,16,39,1,160,20,"Idhaloke parattha {cā}ti imasmiṃ loke yaṃ appamajjanaṃ, tattha diṭṭhadhammike atthe, paraloke yaṃ appamajjanaṃ tattha samparāyike atthe appamattassa me satoti attho. "
