478102,109,1797,55,63,1,66,7,Acchindanto puraṃ {mamā}ti mama bārāṇasinagaraṃ balakkārena gaṇhanto. 
478103,109,1798,2,40,1,312,34,"Tatrāyaṃ anupubbikathā– mahāsatto hi tadā nagarassa catūsu dvāresu catasso majjhe ekaṃ nivesanadvāre ekanti cha dānasālāyo kāretvā kapaṇaddhikādīnaṃ dānaṃ deti, sīlaṃ rakkhati, uposathakammaṃ karoti, khantimettānuddayasampanno aṅke nisinnaṃ puttaṃ paritosayamāno viya sabbasatte paritosayamāno dhammena rajjaṃ kāreti. "
