478106,109,1798,53,89,1,206,28,"Rājā pariggaṇhanto taṃ attanā paccakkhato ñatvā taṃ amaccaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ andhabāla, ayuttaṃ te kataṃ, na tvaṃ mama vijite vasituṃ arahasi, attano dhanañca puttadārañca gahetvā aññattha yāhī’’ ti raṭṭhā pabbājesi. "
