478159,109,1822,2,4,1,26,2,15 . Mahālomahaṃsacariyāvaṇṇanā 
478160,109,1823,2,18,1,59,7,119. Pannarasame ‘‘ susāne seyyaṃ kappemī’’ ti etthāyaṃ anupubbikathā– 
478161,109,1824,2,52,1,504,45,Mahāsatto hi tadā mahati uḷārabhoge kule nibbattitvā vuddhimanvāya disāpāmokkhassa ācariyassa santike garuvāsaṃ vasanto sabbasippānaṃ nipphattiṃ patvā kulagharaṃ āgantvā mātāpitūnaṃ accayena ñātakehi‘‘ kuṭumbaṃ saṇṭhapehī’’ ti yāciyamānopi aniccatāmanasikāramukhena sabbabhavesu abhivaḍḍhamānasaṃvego kāye ca asubhasaññaṃ paṭilabhitvā gharāvāsapalibodhādhibhūtaṃ kilesagahanaṃ anogāhetvāva cirakālasamparicitaṃ nekkhammajjhāsayaṃ upabrūhayamāno mahantaṃ bhogakkhandhaṃ pahāya pabbajitukāmo hutvā puna cintesi–
478162,109,1824,53,63,1,55,5,"‘‘ sacāhaṃ pabbajissāmi, guṇasambhāvanāpākaṭo bhavissāmī’’ ti. "
478163,109,1825,2,44,1,382,34,So lābhasakkāraṃ jigucchanto pabbajjaṃ anupagantvā‘‘ pahomi cāhaṃ lābhālābhādīsu nibbikāro hotun’’ ti attānaṃ takkento‘‘ visesato paraparibhavasahanādipaṭipadaṃ pūrento upekkhāpāramiṃ matthakaṃ pāpessāmī’’ ti nivatthavattheneva gehato nikkhamitvā paramasallekhavuttikopi abalabalo amandamando viya paresaṃ acittakarūpena hīḷitaparibhūto hutvā gāmanigamarājadhānīsu ekarattivāseneva vicarati. 
478164,109,1825,45,54,1,65,8,"Yattha pana mahantaṃ paribhavaṃ paṭilabhati, tattha cirampi vasati. "
478165,109,1825,55,66,1,119,11,So nivatthavatthe jiṇṇe pilotikakhaṇḍena tasmimpi jiṇṇe kenaci dinnaṃ aggaṇhanto hirikopīnapaṭicchādanamatteneva carati. 
478166,109,1825,67,73,1,44,6,Evaṃ gacchante kāle ekaṃ nigamagāmaṃ agamāsi. 
478167,109,1826,2,19,1,159,17,Tattha gāmadārakā dhuttajātikā vedhaverā keci rājavallabhānaṃ puttanattudāsādayo ca uddhatā unnaḷā capalā mukharā vikiṇṇavācā kālena kālaṃ kīḷābahulā vicaranti. 
478168,109,1826,20,44,1,198,21,"Duggate mahallake purise ca itthiyo ca gacchante disvā bhasmapuṭena piṭṭhiyaṃ ākiranti, ketakīpaṇṇaṃ kacchantare olambenti, tena vippakārena parivattetvā olokente yathāvajjakīḷitaṃ dassetvā upahasanti. "
478169,109,1826,45,68,1,138,18,Mahāpuriso tasmiṃ nigame te evaṃ vicarante dhuttadārake disvā‘‘ laddho vata dāni me upekkhāpāramiyā paripūraṇūpāyo’’ ti cintetvā tattha vihāsi. 
478170,109,1826,69,76,1,55,7,Taṃ te dhuttadārakā passitvā vippakāraṃ kātuṃ ārabhanti. 
478171,109,1827,2,13,1,72,11,Mahāsatto taṃ asahanto viya ca tehi bhāyanto viya ca uṭṭhahitvā gacchati. 
478172,109,1827,14,17,1,19,3,Te taṃ anubandhanti. 
478173,109,1827,18,36,1,104,14,So tehi anubandhiyamāno‘‘ ettha natthi koci paṭivattā’’ ti susānaṃ gantvā aṭṭhikaṃ sīsūpadhānaṃ katvā sayati. 
478174,109,1827,37,45,1,85,8,Dhuttadārakāpi tattha gantvā oṭṭhubhanādikaṃ nānappakāraṃ vippakāraṃ katvā pakkamanti. 
478175,109,1827,46,52,1,33,6,Evaṃ te divase divase karonti eva. 
478176,109,1827,53,62,1,45,8,"Ye pana viññū purisā, te evaṃ karonte passanti. "
478177,109,1827,63,80,1,94,13,Te te paṭibāhitvā‘‘ ayaṃ mahānubhāvo tapassī mahāyogī’’ ti ca ñatvā uḷāraṃ sakkārasammānaṃ karonti. 
478178,109,1827,81,87,1,56,6,Mahāsatto pana sabbattha ekasadisova hoti majjhattabhūto. 
478179,109,1827,88,98,1,40,6,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ susāne seyyaṃ kappemī’’ tiādi. 
478180,109,1828,2,34,1,251,28,"Tattha susāne seyyaṃ kappemi, chavaṭṭhikaṃ {upanidhāyā}ti āmakasusāne chaḍḍitakaḷevarato soṇasiṅgālādīhi tahiṃ tahiṃ vikkhittesu aṭṭhikesu ekaṃ aṭṭhikaṃ sīsūpadhānaṃ katvā sucimhi ca asucimhi ca samānacittatāya tasmiṃ susāne seyyaṃ kappemi, sayāmīti attho. "
478181,109,1828,35,38,1,22,2,{Gāmaṇḍalā}ti gāmadārakā. 
478182,109,1828,39,53,1,167,14,Rūpaṃ dassentinappakan ti yathāvajjakīḷitāya oṭṭhubhanaupahasanaummihanādīhi kaṇṇasote salākappavesanādīhi ca atikakkhaḷaṃ anappakaṃ nānappakāraṃ rūpaṃ vikāraṃ karonti. 
478183,109,1829,2,11,1,36,5,120. {Apare}ti tesu eva gāmadārakesu ekacce. 
478184,109,1829,12,45,1,229,27,"{Upāyanānūpanentī}ti‘‘ ayaṃ imesu paribhavavasena evarūpaṃ vippakāraṃ karontesu na kiñci vikāraṃ dasseti, sammānane nu kho kīdiso’’ ti pariggaṇhantā vividhaṃ bahuṃ gandhamālaṃ bhojanaṃ aññāni ca upāyanāni paṇṇākārāni upanenti upaharanti. "
478185,109,1829,46,98,1,355,41,"Aparehi vā tehi anācāragāmadārakehi aññe viññū manussā‘‘ ayaṃ imesaṃ evaṃ vividhampi vippakāraṃ karontānaṃ na kuppati, aññadatthu khantimettānuddayaṃyeva tesu upaṭṭhapeti, aho acchariyapuriso’’ ti haṭṭhā‘‘ bahu vatimehi etasmiṃ vippaṭipajjantehi apuññaṃ pasutan’’ ti saṃviggamānasāva hutvā bahuṃ gandhamālaṃ vividhaṃ bhojanaṃ aññāni ca upāyanāni upanenti upaharanti. "
478186,109,1830,2,17,1,81,10,121. Ye me dukkhaṃ {upaharantī}ti ye gāmadārakā mayhaṃ sarīradukkhaṃ upaharanti upanenti.
