478369,109,1907,30,53,1,185,18,"Ñāṇasaccaṃ vatvā sambhāresu pavattiniṭṭhāpanavacanato‘‘ yathābhūtañāṇavā hi bodhisambhāre adhiṭṭhāti, te ca niṭṭhāpeti paṭipakkhehi akampiyabhāvato’’ ti saccassa anantaraṃ adhiṭṭhānaṃ vuttaṃ. "
478370,109,1907,54,68,1,136,10,Mettāya parahitakaraṇasamādānādhiṭṭhānasiddhito adhiṭṭhānaṃ vatvā hitūpasaṃhāravacanato‘‘ bodhisambhāre hi adhitiṭṭhamāno mettāvihārī hoti’’. 
478371,109,1907,69,77,1,94,8,Acalādhiṭṭhānassa samādānāvikopanena samādānasambhavato ca adhiṭṭhānassa anantaraṃ mettā vuttā. 
478372,109,1907,78,99,1,248,21,Upekkhāya mettāvisuddhito sattesu hitūpasaṃhāraṃ vatvā tadaparādhesu udāsīnatāvacanato mettābhāvanaṃ vatvā tannissandabhāvanāvacanato hitakāmasattepi upekkhakoti acchariyaguṇatāvacanato ca mettāya anantaraṃ upekkhā vuttāti evametāsaṃ kamo veditabbo. 
478373,109,1908,2,27,1,246,18,"Kāni {lakkhaṇarasapaccupaṭṭhānapadaṭṭhānānī}ti ettha avisesena tāva sabbāpi pāramiyo parānuggahalakkhaṇā, paresaṃ upakārakaraṇarasā, avikampanarasā vā, hitesitāpaccupaṭṭhānā, buddhattapaccupaṭṭhānā vā, mahākaruṇāpadaṭṭhānā, karuṇūpāyakosallapadaṭṭhānā vā. "
478374,109,1909,2,15,1,201,12,"Visesena pana yasmā karuṇūpāyakosallapariggahitā attūpakaraṇapariccāgacetanā dānapāramitā, karuṇūpāyakosallapariggahitaṃ kāyavacīsucaritaṃ atthato akattabbaviratikattabbakaraṇacetanādayo ca sīlapāramitā. "
478375,109,1909,16,27,1,186,9,"Karuṇūpāyakosallapariggahito ādīnavadassanapubbaṅgamo kāmabhavehi nikkhamanacittuppādo nekkhammapāramitā, karuṇūpāyakosallapariggahito dhammānaṃ sāmaññavisesalakkhaṇāvabodho paññāpāramitā . "
478376,109,1909,28,64,1,565,30,"Karuṇūpāyakosallapariggahito kāyacittehi parahitārambho vīriyapāramitā, karuṇūpāyakosallapariggahitaṃ sattasaṅkhārāparādhasahanaṃ adosappadhāno tadākārappavattacittuppādo khantipāramitā, karuṇūpāyakosallapariggahitaṃ viraticetanādibhedaṃ avisaṃvādanaṃ saccapāramitā, karuṇūpāyakosallapariggahitaṃ acalasamādānādhiṭṭhānaṃ tadākārappavatto cittuppādo adhiṭṭhānapāramitā, karuṇūpāyakosallapariggahito lokassa hitasukhūpasaṃhāro atthato abyāpādo mettāpāramitā, karuṇūpāyakosallapariggahitā anunayapaṭighaviddhaṃsanī iṭṭhāniṭṭhesu sattasaṅkhāresu samappavatti upekkhāpāramitā. "
478377,109,1910,2,15,1,157,9,"Tasmā pariccāgalakkhaṇā dānapāramī, deyyadhamme lobhaviddhaṃsanarasā, anāsattipaccupaṭṭhānā, bhavavibhavasampattipaccupaṭṭhānā vā, pariccajitabbavatthupadaṭṭhānā. "
478378,109,1910,16,25,1,79,7,"Sīlanalakkhaṇā sīlapāramī, samādhānalakkhaṇā patiṭṭhānalakkhaṇā cāti vuttaṃ hoti. "
478379,109,1910,26,34,1,81,5,"Dussīlyaviddhaṃsanarasā, anavajjarasā vā, soceyyapaccupaṭṭhānā, hirottappapadaṭṭhānā. "
478380,109,1910,35,49,1,132,11,"Kāmato ca bhavato ca nikkhamanalakkhaṇā nekkhammapāramī, tadādīnavavibhāvanarasā, tato eva vimukhabhāvapaccupaṭṭhānā, saṃvegapadaṭṭhānā. "
478381,109,1910,50,70,1,223,15,"Yathāsabhāvapaṭivedhalakkhaṇā paññāpāramī, akkhalitapaṭivedhalakkhaṇā vā kusalissāsakhittausupaṭivedho viya, visayobhāsanarasā padīpo viya, asammohapaccupaṭṭhānā araññagatasudesiko viya, samādhipadaṭṭhānā, catusaccapadaṭṭhānā vā. "
478382,109,1910,71,82,1,119,7,"Ussāhalakkhaṇā vīriyapāramī, upatthambhanarasā, asaṃsīdanapaccupaṭṭhānā, vīriyārambhavatthupadaṭṭhānā, saṃvegapadaṭṭhānā vā. "
478383,109,1910,83,94,1,127,7,"Khamanalakkhaṇā khantipāramī, iṭṭhāniṭṭhasahanarasā, adhivāsanapaccupaṭṭhānā, avirodhapaccupaṭṭhānā vā, yathābhūtadassanapadaṭṭhānā. "
478384,109,1910,95,103,1,97,5,"Avisaṃvādanalakkhaṇā saccapāramī, yathāsabhāvavibhāvanarasā, sādhutāpaccupaṭṭhānā, soraccapadaṭṭhānā. "
478385,109,1910,104,115,1,134,8,"Bodhisambhāresu adhiṭṭhānalakkhaṇā adhiṭṭhānapāramī, tesaṃ paṭipakkhābhibhavanarasā, tattha acalatāpaccupaṭṭhānā, bodhisambhārapadaṭṭhānā. "
478386,109,1910,116,128,1,138,8,"Hitākārappavattilakkhaṇā mettāpāramī, hitūpasaṃhārarasā, āghātavinayanarasā vā, sommabhāvapaccupaṭṭhānā, sattānaṃ manāpabhāvadassanapadaṭṭhānā. "
