478428,109,1925,2,41,1,262,31,"Tatridaṃ chandamahantatāya opammaṃ– yo sakalacakkavāḷagabbhaṃ ekodakībhūtaṃ attano bāhubaleneva uttaritvā pāraṃ gantuṃ samattho, so buddhattaṃ pāpuṇātīti sutvā taṃ dukkarato adahanto‘‘ ahaṃ taṃ uttaritvā pāraṃ gamissāmī’’ ti chandajāto hoti, na tattha saṅkocaṃ āpajjati. "
