479172,110,75,2,11,1,49,8,"Na tikicchāpeti taṃ byādhiṃ, na doso so tikicchake."
479173,110,76,2,9,1,39,5,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ kilesabyādhīhi, dukkhito paripīḷito; "
479174,110,77,2,14,1,47,9,"Na gavesati taṃ ācariyaṃ, na doso so vināyake’’ ti. "
479175,110,78,2,23,1,168,19,"Aparampi cintesi– yathā maṇḍanajātiko puriso kaṇṭhe āsattaṃ kuṇapaṃ chaḍḍetvā sukhī gacchati, evaṃ mayāpi imaṃ pūtikāyaṃ chaḍḍetvā anapekkhena nibbānanagaraṃ pavisitabbaṃ. "
479176,110,78,24,56,1,253,30,"Yathā ca naranāriyo ukkārabhūmiyaṃ uccārapassāvaṃ katvā na taṃ ucchaṅgena vā ādāya dasantena vā veṭhetvā gacchanti, jigucchamānā pana anapekkhāva chaḍḍetvā gacchanti, evaṃ mayāpi imaṃ pūtikāyaṃ anapekkhena chaḍḍetvā amataṃ nibbānanagaraṃ pavisituṃ vaṭṭati. "
479177,110,78,57,78,1,165,20,"Yathā ca nāvikā nāma jajjaraṃ nāvaṃ anapekkhā chaḍḍetvā gacchanti, evaṃ ahampi imaṃ navahi vaṇamukhehi paggharantaṃ kāyaṃ chaḍḍetvā anapekkho nibbānapuraṃ pavisissāmi. "
479178,110,78,79,100,1,174,20,"Yathā ca puriso nānāratanāni ādāya corehi saddhiṃ maggaṃ gacchanto attano ratananāsabhayena te chaḍḍetvā khemaṃ maggaṃ gaṇhāti, evaṃ ayampi karajakāyo ratanavilopakacorasadiso. "
479179,110,78,101,109,1,74,7,"Sacāhaṃ ettha taṇhaṃ karissāmi, ariyamaggakusaladhammaratanaṃ me nassissati. "
479180,110,78,110,119,1,78,9,Tasmā mayā imaṃ corasadisaṃ kāyaṃ chaḍḍetvā nibbānanagaraṃ pavisituṃ vaṭṭatīti. 
