479216,110,110,2,22,1,129,15,"Tattha ‘‘ assamo sukato mayhaṃ, paṇṇasālā sumāpitā’’ ti imāya pāḷiyā sumedhapaṇḍitena assamapaṇṇasālācaṅkamā sahatthā māpitā viya vuttā. "
479217,110,110,23,45,1,158,17,Ayaṃ panettha attho– mahāsattaṃ‘‘ himavantaṃ ajjhogāhetvā ajja dhammikaṃ pabbataṃ pavisissāmī’’ ti nikkhantaṃ disvā sakko devānamindo vissakammadevaputtaṃ āmantesi–
479218,110,110,46,61,1,80,9,"‘‘ tāta, ayaṃ sumedhapaṇḍito pabbajissāmīti nikkhanto, etassa vasanaṭṭhānaṃ māpehī’’ ti. "
479219,110,110,62,75,1,97,11,"So tassa vacanaṃ sampaṭicchitvā ramaṇīyaṃ assamaṃ, suguttaṃ paṇṇasālaṃ, manoramaṃ caṅkamañca māpesi. "
479220,110,110,76,89,1,108,12,"Bhagavā pana tadā attano puññānubhāvena nipphannaṃ taṃ assamapadaṃ sandhāya sāriputta, tasmiṃ dhammikapabbate–"
