479368,110,190,2,20,1,137,16,"Manussattabhāvasmiṃyeva hi ṭhatvā buddhattaṃ patthentassa patthanā samijjhati, na nāgassa vā supaṇṇassa vā devatāya vā patthanā samijjhati. "
479369,110,190,21,34,1,133,12,"Manussattabhāvepi purisaliṅge ṭhitasseva patthanā samijjhati, na itthiyā vā paṇḍakanapuṃsakaubhatobyañjanakānaṃ vā patthanā samijjhati. "
479370,110,190,35,45,1,95,9,"Purisassāpi tasmiṃ attabhāve arahattappattiyā hetusampannasseva patthanā samijjhati, no itarassa. "
479371,110,190,46,62,1,156,15,"Hetusampannassāpi jīvamānakabuddhasseva santike patthentassa patthanā samijjhati, parinibbute buddhe cetiyasantike vā bodhimūle vā patthentassa na samijjhati. "
479372,110,190,63,74,1,90,9,"Buddhānaṃ santike patthentassāpi pabbajjāliṅge ṭhitasseva samijjhati, no gihiliṅge ṭhitassa. "
479373,110,190,75,84,1,102,8,"Pabbajitassāpi pañcābhiññassa aṭṭhasamāpattilābhinoyeva samijjhati, na imāya guṇasampattiyā virahitassa. "
479374,110,190,85,101,1,131,14,"Guṇasampannenāpi yena attano jīvitaṃ buddhānaṃ pariccattaṃ hoti, tassa iminā adhikārena adhikārasampannasseva samijjhati, na itarassa. "
479375,110,190,102,121,1,140,17,"Adhikārasampannassāpi yassa buddhakārakadhammānaṃ atthāya mahanto chando ca ussāho ca vāyāmo ca pariyeṭṭhi ca, tasseva samijjhati, na itarassa. "
479376,110,191,2,25,1,164,18,"Tatridaṃ chandamahantatāya opammaṃ– sace hi evamassa‘‘ yo sakalacakkavāḷagabbhaṃ ekodakībhūtaṃ attano bāhubalena uttaritvā pāraṃ gantuṃ samattho , so buddhattaṃ pāpuṇāti. "
479377,110,191,26,42,1,133,15,"Yo vā pana sakalacakkavāḷagabbhaṃ veḷugumbasañchannaṃ byūhitvā madditvā padasā gacchanto pāraṃ gantuṃ samattho, so buddhattaṃ pāpuṇāti. "
479378,110,191,43,60,1,145,16,"Yo vā pana sakalacakkavāḷagabbhaṃ sattiyo ākoṭetvā nirantaraṃ sattiphalasamākiṇṇaṃ padasā akkamamāno pāraṃ gantuṃ samattho, so buddhattaṃ pāpuṇāti. "
479379,110,191,61,78,1,121,14,"Yo vā pana sakalacakkavāḷagabbhaṃ vītaccitaṅgārabharitaṃ pādehi maddamāno pāraṃ gantuṃ samattho, so buddhattaṃ pāpuṇātī’’ ti. "
479380,110,191,79,119,1,216,33,"Yo etesu ekampi attano dukkaraṃ na maññati,‘‘ ahaṃ etampi taritvā vā gantvā vā pāraṃ gahessāmī’’ ti evaṃ mahantena chandena ca ussāhena ca vāyāmena ca pariyeṭṭhiyā ca samannāgato hoti, tassa patthanā samijjhati, na itarassa. "
479381,110,191,120,130,1,88,10,Sumedhatāpaso pana ime aṭṭha dhamme samodhānetvā buddhabhāvāya abhinīhāraṃ katvā nipajji. 
479382,110,192,2,60,1,447,47,"Dīpaṅkaropi bhagavā āgantvā sumedhatāpasassa sīsabhāge ṭhatvā maṇisīhapañjaraṃ ugghāṭento viya pañcavaṇṇappasādasampannāni akkhīni ummīletvā kalalapiṭṭhe nipannaṃ sumedhatāpasaṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ tāpaso buddhattāya abhinīhāraṃ katvā nipanno, ijjhissati nu kho imassa patthanā, udāhu no’’ ti anāgataṃsañāṇaṃ pesetvā upadhārento‘‘ ito kappasatasahassādhikāni cattāri asaṅkhyeyyāni atikkamitvā gotamo nāma buddho bhavissatī’’ ti ñatvā ṭhitakova parisamajjhe byākāsi–"
479383,110,192,61,74,1,65,9,‘‘ passatha no tumhe imaṃ uggatapaṃ tāpasaṃ kalalapiṭṭhe nipannan’’ ti?
479384,110,192,75,83,1,14,3,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bhante’’ ti."
479385,110,192,84,105,1,164,17,"‘‘ Ayaṃ buddhattāya abhinīhāraṃ katvā nipanno, samijjhissati imassa patthanā, ito kappasatasahassādhikānaṃ catunnaṃ asaṅkhyeyyānaṃ matthake gotamo nāma buddho bhavissati. "
479386,110,192,106,168,1,459,51,"Tasmiṃ panassa attabhāve kapilavatthu nāma nagaraṃ nivāso bhavissati, māyā nāma devī mātā, suddhodano nāma rājā pitā, aggasāvako upatisso nāma thero, dutiyasāvako kolito nāma, buddhupaṭṭhāko ānando nāma, aggasāvikā khemā nāma therī, dutiyasāvikā uppalavaṇṇā nāma therī bhavissati, paripakkañāṇo mahābhinikkhamanaṃ katvā mahāpadhānaṃ padahitvā nigrodhamūle pāyāsaṃ paṭiggahetvā nerañjarāya tīre paribhuñjitvā bodhimaṇḍaṃ āruyha assattharukkhamūle abhisambujjhissatī’’ ti. "
479387,110,192,169,171,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
479388,110,193,2,9,1,37,5,"‘ ‘ Dīpaṅkaro lokavidū, āhutīnaṃ paṭiggaho; "
479389,110,194,2,8,1,40,5,"Ussīsake maṃ ṭhatvāna, idaṃ vacanamabravi."
479390,110,195,2,9,1,41,6,"‘ Passatha imaṃ tāpasaṃ, jaṭilaṃ uggatāpanaṃ; "
479391,110,196,2,9,1,43,6,"Aparimeyye ito kappe, buddho loke bhavissati."
479392,110,197,2,10,1,43,6,"‘ Ahu kapilavhayā rammā, nikkhamitvā tathāgato; "
479393,110,198,2,7,1,41,4,"Padhānaṃ padahitvāna, katvā dukkarakārikaṃ."
479394,110,199,2,7,1,37,4,"‘ Ajapālarukkhamūle, nisīditvā tathāgato; "
479395,110,200,2,7,1,41,4,"Tattha pāyāsaṃ paggayha, nerañjaramupehiti."
479396,110,201,2,10,1,39,7,"‘ Nerañjarāya tīramhi, pāyāsaṃ ada so jino; "
479397,110,202,2,5,1,38,2,"Paṭiyattavaramaggena , bodhimūlamūpehiti."
479398,110,203,2,10,1,43,6,"‘ Tato padakkhiṇaṃ katvā, bodhimaṇḍaṃ anuttaro; "
479399,110,204,2,6,1,42,3,"Assattharukkhamūlamhi , bujjhissati mahāyaso."
479400,110,205,2,10,1,39,7,"‘ Imassa janikā mātā, māyā nāma bhavissati; "
479401,110,206,2,9,1,40,6,"Pitā suddhodano nāma, ayaṃ hessati gotamo."
479402,110,207,2,8,1,36,5,"‘ Anāsavā vītarāgā, santacittā samāhitā; "
479403,110,208,2,9,1,39,6,"Kolito upatisso ca, aggā hessanti sāvakā; "
479404,110,209,2,8,1,42,5,"Ānando nāmupaṭṭhāko, upaṭṭhissati taṃ jinaṃ."
479405,110,210,2,11,1,41,7,"‘ Khemā uppalavaṇṇā ca, aggā hessanti sāvikā; "
479406,110,211,2,7,1,36,4,"Anāsavā vītarāgā, santacittā samāhitā; "
479407,110,212,2,12,1,45,6,"Bodhi tassa bhagavato, assatthoti pavuccatī’’’ ti. "
479408,110,213,2,14,1,73,8,Sumedhatāpaso ‘‘ mayhaṃ kira patthanā samijjhissatī’’ ti somanassappatto ahosi. 
479409,110,213,15,30,1,108,11,Mahājano dīpaṅkaradasabalassa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ sumedhatāpaso kira buddhabījaṃ buddhaṅkuro’’ ti haṭṭhatuṭṭho ahosi. 
479410,110,213,31,71,1,298,34,"Evañcassa ahosi‘‘ yathā nāma puriso nadiṃ taranto ujukena titthena uttarituṃ asakkonto heṭṭhātitthena uttarati, evameva mayampi dīpaṅkaradasabalassa sāsane maggaphalaṃ alabhamānā anāgate yadā tvaṃ buddho bhavissasi, tadā tava sammukhā maggaphalaṃ sacchikātuṃ samatthā bhaveyyāmā’’ ti patthanaṃ ṭhapayiṃsu. "
479411,110,213,72,94,1,207,21,"Dīpaṅkaradasabalopi bodhisattaṃ pasaṃsitvā aṭṭhahi pupphamuṭṭhīhi pūjetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi, tepi catusatasahassasaṅkhā khīṇāsavā bodhisattaṃ gandhehi ca mālehi ca pūjetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkamiṃsu. "
479412,110,213,95,101,1,50,6,Devamanussā pana tatheva pūjetvā vanditvā pakkantā. 
479413,110,214,2,18,1,120,12,Bodhisatto sabbesaṃ paṭikkantakāle sayanā vuṭṭhāya‘‘ pāramiyo vicinissāmī’’ ti puppharāsimatthake pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā nisīdi. 
479414,110,214,19,83,1,453,48,"Evaṃ nisinne bodhisatte sakaladasasahassacakkavāḷadevatā sannipatitvā sādhukāraṃ datvā‘‘ ayya sumedhatāpasa, porāṇakabodhisattānaṃ pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā‘ pāramiyo vicinissāmā’ ti nisinnakāle yāni pubbanimittāni nāma paññāyanti, tāni sabbānipi ajja pātubhūtāni, nissaṃsayena tvaṃ buddho bhavissasi , mayampetaṃ jānāma‘ yassetāni nimittāni paññāyanti, ekantena so buddho hoti’, tvaṃ attano vīriyaṃ daḷhaṃ katvā paggaṇhā’’ ti bodhisattaṃ nānappakārāhi thutīhi abhitthuniṃsu. "
