479509,110,306,2,48,1,284,33,"So ‘‘ dhuvāhaṃ buddho bhavissāmī’’ ti evaṃ katasanniṭṭhāno buddhakārake dhamme upadhāretuṃ‘‘ kahaṃ nu kho buddhakārakadhammā, kiṃ uddhaṃ, udāhu adho, disāsu, vidisāsū’’ ti anukkamena sakalaṃ dhammadhātuṃ vicinanto porāṇakabodhisattehi āsevitanisevitaṃ paṭhamaṃ dānapāramiṃ disvā evaṃ attānaṃ ovadi–"
479510,110,306,49,59,1,63,7,"‘‘ sumedhapaṇḍita, tvaṃ ito paṭṭhāya paṭhamaṃ dānapāramiṃ pūreyyāsi. "
479511,110,306,60,103,1,309,38,"Yathā hi nikkujjito udakakumbho nissesaṃ katvā udakaṃ vamatiyeva, na paccāharati, evameva dhanaṃ vā yasaṃ vā puttaṃ vā dāraṃ vā aṅgapaccaṅgaṃ vā anoloketvā sampattayācakānaṃ sabbaṃ icchiticchitaṃ nissesaṃ katvā dadamāno bodhirukkhamūle nisīditvā buddho bhavissasī’’ ti paṭhamaṃ dānapāramiṃ daḷhaṃ katvā adhiṭṭhāsi. "
479512,110,306,104,106,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
