479667,110,423,23,69,1,271,38,"Mahājano bhītatasito satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho bhagavā nāgāvaṭṭo ayaṃ bhūtayakkhadevatāsu aññatarāvaṭṭoti na hi mayaṃ etaṃ jānāma, apica kho sabbopi ayaṃ mahājano upadduto, kiṃ nu kho imassa lokassa pāpakaṃ bhavissati, udāhu kalyāṇaṃ, kathetha no etaṃ kāraṇan’’ ti āha. "
479668,110,423,70,87,1,91,14,"Atha satthā tesaṃ kathaṃ sutvā‘‘ tumhe mā bhāyatha mā cintayittha, natthi vo itonidānaṃ bhayaṃ. "
