479773,110,518,2,14,1,97,11,Dīpaṅkarassa pana bhagavato aparabhāge ekaṃ asaṅkhyeyyaṃ atikkamitvā koṇḍañño nāma satthā udapādi. 
479774,110,518,15,19,1,35,4,Tassāpi tayo sāvakasannipātā ahesuṃ. 
479775,110,518,20,28,1,73,6,"Paṭhamasannipāte koṭisatasahassaṃ, dutiye koṭisahassaṃ, tatiye navutikoṭiyo. "
479776,110,518,29,40,1,122,11,Tadā bodhisatto vijitāvī nāma cakkavattī hutvā koṭisatasahassasaṅkhassa buddhappamukhassa bhikkhusaṅghassa mahādānaṃ adāsi. 
479777,110,518,41,53,1,65,8,Satthā bodhisattaṃ‘‘ buddho bhavissasī’’ ti byākaritvā dhammaṃ desesi. 
479778,110,518,54,61,1,54,7,So satthu dhammakathaṃ sutvā rajjaṃ niyyādetvā pabbaji. 
479779,110,518,62,76,1,109,13,So tīṇi piṭakāni uggahetvā aṭṭha samāpattiyo pañca abhiññāyo ca uppādetvā aparihīnajjhāno brahmaloke nibbatti. 
479780,110,518,77,120,1,279,35,"Koṇḍaññassa buddhassa pana rammavatī nāma nagaraṃ, sunando nāma khattiyo pitā, sujātā nāma devī mātā, bhaddo ca subhaddo ca dve aggasāvakā, anuruddho nāmupaṭṭhāko, tissā ca upatissā ca dve aggasāvikā, sālakalyāṇī bodhi, aṭṭhāsītihatthubbedhaṃ sarīraṃ, vassasatasahassaṃ āyuppamāṇaṃ ahosi."
479781,110,519,2,10,1,41,6,"‘ ‘ Dīpaṅkarassa aparena, koṇḍañño nāma nāyako; "
479782,110,520,2,10,1,42,5,"Anantatejo amitayaso, appameyyo durāsado’’ ti. "
479783,110,521,2,20,1,122,14,"Tassa aparabhāge ekaṃ asaṅkhyeyyaṃ atikkamitvā ekasmiṃyeva kappe caturo buddhā nibbattiṃsu maṅgalo, sumano, revato, {sobhito}ti. "
479784,110,521,21,26,1,42,5,Maṅgalassa bhagavato tayo sannipātā ahesuṃ. 
479785,110,521,27,38,1,93,9,"Tesu paṭhamasannipāte koṭisatasahassaṃ bhikkhū ahesuṃ, dutiye koṭisahassaṃ, tatiye navutikoṭiyo. "
479786,110,521,39,50,1,119,11,Vemātikabhātā kirassa ānandakumāro nāma navutikoṭisaṅkhāya parisāya saddhiṃ dhammassavanatthāya satthu santikaṃ agamāsi. 
479787,110,521,51,64,1,94,12,"Satthā tassa anupubbiṃ kathaṃ kathesi, so saddhiṃ parisāya saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. "
479788,110,521,65,84,1,137,14,"Satthā tesaṃ kulaputtānaṃ pubbacaritaṃ olokento iddhimayapattacīvarassa upanissayaṃ disvā dakkhiṇahatthaṃ pasāretvā‘‘ etha, bhikkhavo’’ ti āha. "
479789,110,521,85,95,1,125,10,Sabbe taṅkhaṇaññeva iddhimayapattacīvaradharā saṭṭhivassamahātherā viya ākappasampannā hutvā satthāraṃ vanditvā parivārayiṃsu. 
479790,110,521,96,100,1,37,4,Ayamassa tatiyo sāvakasannipāto ahosi. 
