479794,110,522,37,48,1,104,10,"Ettakaṃ kālaṃ candimasūriyādayo attano pabhāya virocituṃ nāsakkhiṃsu, rattindivaparicchedo na paññāyittha. "
479795,110,522,49,68,1,157,15,"Divā sūriyālokena viya sattā niccaṃ buddhālokeneva vicariṃsu, sāyaṃ pupphitakusumānaṃ, pāto ravanakasakuṇādīnañca vasena loko rattindivaparicchedaṃ sallakkhesi. "
479796,110,523,2,8,1,48,6,Kiṃ pana aññesaṃ buddhānaṃ ayamānubhāvo natthīti? 
479797,110,523,9,11,1,9,2,No natthi. 
479798,110,523,12,23,1,78,11,Tepi hi ākaṅkhamānā dasasahassiṃ vā lokadhātuṃ tato vā bhiyyo ābhāya phareyyuṃ. 
479799,110,523,24,36,1,136,12,Maṅgalassa pana bhagavato pubbapatthanāvasena aññesaṃ byāmappabhā viya sarīrappabhā niccakālameva dasasahassilokadhātuṃ pharitvā aṭṭhāsi. 
479800,110,523,37,47,1,105,10,So kira bodhisattacariyakāle vessantarasadise attabhāve ṭhito saputtadāro vaṅkapabbatasadise pabbate vasi. 
479801,110,523,48,61,1,124,13,Atheko kharadāṭhiko nāma yakkho mahāpurisassa dānajjhāsayataṃ sutvā brāhmaṇavaṇṇena upasaṅkamitvā mahāsattaṃ dve dārake yāci. 
