479845,110,530,36,40,1,36,4,Athassa maṇḍapaṃ olokayato etadahosi–
479846,110,530,41,69,1,165,22,"‘‘ nāyaṃ maṇḍapo manussabhūtena kato, mayhaṃ pana ajjhāsayaṃ mayhaṃ guṇaṃ āgamma addhā sakkabhavanaṃ uṇhaṃ ahosi, tato sakkena devaraññā ayaṃ maṇḍapo kārito bhavissatī’’ ti."
